e%20presumably%20functions%20in%20a%20manner%20similar%20to%20a%20system%20professionally%20built%20to%20military%20specifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20mobile%20rocket%20artillery%2C%20it%20features%20a%20single%20platform%20supporting%20a%20collection%20of%20launch%20tubes%20able%20to%20fire%20multiple%20surface-to-surface%20rockets.%20When%20it%20prepares%20to%20launch%2C%20the%20tubes%20rise%20up%20and%20fire%20the%20rockets.%20They%20launch%20from%20the%20front%2C%20while%20the%20back%20of%20the%20tubes%20will%20release%20the%20exhaust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226708%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20civilian%20volunteers%20work%20to%20modify%20damaged%20and%20salvaged%20vehicles%20into%20small%20mobile%20MLRS%20(Multiple%20Launch%20Rocket%20System)%20units%20made%20from%20recovered%20Russian%20and%20Ukrainian%20military%20hardware%20on%20September%2025%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65170bbd3fb8f400198ad760%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224474%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20six%20tubes%20that%20would%20hold%20the%20MLRS'%20rockets.%3Cp%3EChris%20McGrath%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-mlrs-rocket-artillery-ukraine-wants-from-the-us-2022-5%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20US%20for%20MLRS%20in%20May%202022%2C%20arguing%20the%20longer-range%20weapons%20would%20give%20troops%20the%20ability%20to%20strike%20Russian%20targets%2C%20such%20as%20command%20and%20control%20centers%2C%20troop%20concentrations%2C%20and%20ammunition%20depots%2C%20from%20further%20away.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20was%20hesitant%20to%20give%20Ukraine%20weapons%20that%20could%20be%20used%20to%20strike%20Russian%20territory%2C%20and%20there%20were%20real%20concerns%20about%20escalating%20tensions%20with%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20