08GB%20of%20RAM%20which%20isn't%20enough%20to%20play%20some%20intensive%20games%20without%20lag.%20Call%20of%20Duty%3A%20Warzone%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20recommends%20at%20least%2012GB.%20But%20luckily%20the%20RAM%20is%20customizable%2C%20meaning%20you%20can%20add%20up%20to%2064GB%20later.%20Just%20remember%20to%20account%20for%20that%20in%20your%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20got%20some%20flaws%20in%20design%2C%20too.%20The%20G5's%20thermals%20ensure%20that%20you%20won't%20burn%20your%20thighs%20while%20gaming%2C%20but%20its%20fans%20get%20%3Cem%3Eincredibly%3C%2Fem%3E%20loud.%20The%20battery%20life%20is%20poor%20as%20well.%20And%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20aesthetics%2C%20the%20G5%20isn't%20pretty%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20essentially%20a%20plain%20black%20box%20with%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BGigabyte%26quot%3B%20stamped%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gigabyte%20G5%20is%20simple.%20But%20for%20gamers%20wanting%20great%20performance%20on%20a%20budget%2C%20it's%20absolutely%20a%20standout%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20with%20an%20RTX%204050%3A%20MSI%20Bravo%2015%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222633%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20MSI%20Bravo%2015%20laptop%20in%20front%20of%20backdrop%20with%20lava%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65148e251c099d0019ad4c61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221974%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMSI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20More%20RAM%20than%20other%20budget%20models%2C%20cool%20full-sized%20keyboard%2C%20powerful%20RTX%204050%20GPU%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Average%20CPU%2C%20bulky%20design%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMSI%20has%20so%20many%20different%20kinds%20of%20gaming%20laptops%20that%20it's%20often%20hard%20to%20tell%20them%20apart.%20But%20gamers%20looking%20for%20a%20budget%20laptop%20build%20should%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%2015.6-inch%20MSI%20Bravo%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20seen%20this%20Brav