Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fantastic%20graphics%20and%20CPU%2C%20highly%20customizable%2C%20slim%20frame%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Need%20to%20pay%20extra%20for%20a%20good%20screen%2C%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20storage%20space%20or%20ports%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHP%20doesn't%20come%20up%20very%20often%20in%20PC%20gaming%20conversations.%20That's%20unfortunate%2C%20because%20the%20HP%20Victus%2016t-r%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20budget%20gaming%20laptops%20you%20can%20buy.%20It%20offers%20power%20and%20portability%20in%20a%20highly%20customizable%20package%2C%20giving%20it%20an%20edge%20over%20other%20similarly%20priced%20laptops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20let's%20talk%20about%20power.%20For%20about%20%241%2C190%2C%20you%20can%20configure%20a%20Victus%20with%20an%20RTX%204060%20GPU%20and%20a%2013th-gen%20Intel%20i7-13700HX%20CPU.%20That%20graphics%20card%20has%20the%20power%20to%20run%20nearly%20any%20game%20at%20max%20settings%20with%20a%20consistently%20high%20framerate%2C%20including%20with%20ray%20tracing%20and%20DLSS%20frame%20generation.%20And%20the%20i7-13700HX%20is%20beefy%20enough%20for%20heavy%20multitasking%2C%20as%20well%20as%20video%20editing%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20content%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20setup%20also%20gives%20you%2016GB%20of%20RAM%20and%20512GB%20of%20solid%20state%20storage.%20That's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20storage%2C%20especially%20considering%20how%20big%20games%20are%20these%20days%2C%20but%20it's%20upgradable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20flaw%20with%20this%20setup%20is%20the%20screen.%20By%20default%2C%20the%2016t-r's%20screen%20only%20goes%20up%20to%20250%20nits%20in%20brightness%2C%20and%20has%20a%20relatively%20slow%20refresh%20rate%20of%20144Hz.%20I'd%20definitely%20recommend%20splurging%20for%20the%20upgraded%20165Hz%20or%20240Hz%20versions%2C%20which%20are%20only%20%2480%20or%20%24140%20more%2C%20respectively.%20Both%20of%20these%20versions%20are%20brighter%20too%2C%20going%20up%20to%20300%20nits.%20And%20every%20version%20is%2016.1%20inches%2C%20which%20is%20one%20inch%20bigger%20than%20most%20of%20our%20other%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20value%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20beat%20the%20HP%20Victus%2016t-r.%20Try%20to%20buy%20it%20direct%20from%20HP's%20website%2C%20if%20you%20can%20%E2%80%94%20they%20offer%20lots%20of%20customization%20options%20and%20discounts%20that'll%20help%20you%20stay%20within%20your%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20vibrant%20visuals%3A%20Dell%20G15%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Dell%20G15%20laptop%2C%20displaying%20a%20screenshot%20from%20the%20game%20Valorant%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20chair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65146693eee46600193ba3ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Very%20powerful%20CPU%20and%20GPU%2C%20lots%20of%20storage%20space%2C%20can%20be%20configured%20with%20a%20bright%20400-nit%20screen%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20many%20ports%2C%20runs%20hot%20and%20loud%2C%20mediocre%20trackpad%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dell%20G15%20is%20a%20popular%2015.6-inch%20budget%20laptop%2C%20and%20for%20good%20reason%3A%20It's%20an%20inexpensive%20option%20that%20offers%20both%20great%20graphics%20and%20some%20of%20the%20best%20laptop%20CPUs%20you%20can%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20your%20budget%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20the%20Dell%20G15%20with%20an%20RTX%203050%2C%20RTX%204050%2C%20or%20RTX%204060%20GPU%2C%20which%20are%20all%20great%20options.%20But%20the%20G15's%20processor%20is%20where%20it%20truly%20shines%3A%20The%20Dell%20G15%20is%20one%20of%20the%20only%20budget%20laptops%20to%20use%20the%20newest%2013th%20generation%20of%20Intel%20CPUs.%20These%20are%20leagues%20faster%20than%20any%20other%20laptop%20CPUs%20