%20relief%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20next%20step%20includes%20negotiations%20with%20stakeholders%20on%20the%20relief.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20department%20is%20focusing%20on%20five%20groups%20of%20borrowers%20as%20it%20crafts%20the%20new%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20just%20took%20the%20next%20step%20on%20its%20second%20attempt%20to%20get%20broad%20student-debt%20relief%20to%20millions%20of%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ed.gov%2Fpolicy%2Fhighered%2Freg%2Fhearulemaking%2F2023%2Fsession-1--issue-paper-student-loan-reliefom-committee.pdf%3Futm_content%3D%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_name%3D%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%26utm_term%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20outlining%20what%20it%20is%20considering%20as%20it%20develops%20its%20new%20plan%20for%20broad%20student-loan%20forgiveness.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20Biden's%20first%20plan%20to%20cancel%20student%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20the%20HEROES%20Act%20of%202003%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20education%20secretary%20to%20waive%20or%20modify%20student-loan%20balances%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20national%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20the%20HEROES%20Act%20was%20the%20improper%20law%20to%20carry%20out%20relief%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20so%20the%20department%20announced%20it%20would%20be%20trying%20again%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-will-take-cancel-student-debt-higher-education-act-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20does%20not%20require%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20national%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20requires%20the%20administration%20go%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-timeline-for-biden-new-student-debt-relief-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20negotiated%20rulemaking%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20series%20of%20negotiation%20sessions%20and%20periods%20of%20public%20comment.%20The%20department's%20Friday%20announcement%20released%20the%20names%20of%20the%20negotiators%2C%20along%20with%20topics%20the%20negotiations%20will%20focus%20on%20in%20the%20upcoming%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Biden-Harris%20Administration%20has%20taken%20unprecedented%20action%20to%20fix%20the%20broken%20student%20loan%20system%20and%20deliver%20record%20amounts%20of%20student%20debt%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fbiden-harris-administration-moves-forward-student-debt-relief-negotiated-rulemaking-deliver-support-many-borrowers-possible-quickly-possible%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20we%20are%20diligently%20moving%20through%20the%20regulatory%20process%20to%20advance%20debt%20relief%20for%20even%20more%20borrowers.%20Today%2C%20after%20considering%20more%20than%2026%2C000%20public%20comments%20on%20how%20to%20tailor%20this%20relief%2C%20we%20are%20releasing%20this%20additional%20information%20about%20this%20effort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20process%2C%20and%20what%20the%20negotiations%20will%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWho%20are%20the%20negotiators%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20released%20a%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ed.gov%2Fpolicy%2Fhighered%2Freg%2Fhearulemaking%2F2023%2Fstudent-loan-debt-relief-committee-list.pdf%3Futm_content%3D%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_name%3D%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%26utm_term%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E26%20selected%20negotiators%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20participate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20sessions%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20will%20be%20held%20on%20October%2010%20and%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20department%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-timeline-for-biden-new-student-debt-relief-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebegan%20the%20process%20of%20seeking%20nominations%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20people%20to%20serve%20on%20the%20negotiating%20committee.%20They%20were%20nominated%20by%20the%20public%20and%20selected%20by%20the%20department.%20The%20nominee%20categories%20include%20civil%20rights%20organizations%2C%20legal%20assistance%20organizations%2C%20state%20attorneys%20general%2C%20representatives%20of%20federal%20servicers%2C%20and%20student-loan%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20it%20is%20still%20seeking%20nominations%20for%20two%20constituency%20groups%3A%20state%20officials%2C%20and%20Historically%20Black%20Colleges%20and%20Universities%20and%20Minority-Serving%20Institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20will%20be%20discussed%20at%20negotiations%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ed.gov%2Fpolicy%2Fhighered%2Freg%2Fhearulemaking%2F2023%2Fsession-1--issue-paper-student-loan-reliefom-committee.pdf%3Futm_content%3D%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_name%3D%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%26utm_term%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20negotiators%20will%20begin%20discussing%20during%20the%20October%20sessions.%20The%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20states%20the%20education%20secretary%20can%20%26quot%3Benforce%2C%20pay%2C%20compromise%2C%20waive%2C%20or%20release%20any%20right%2C%20title%2C%20claim%2C%20lien%2C%20or%20demand%26quot%3B%20related%20to%20student%20debt%2C%20and%20the%20negotiators%20will%20discuss%20the%20scope%20of%20that%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20also%20said%20the%20department%20is%20%26quot%3Bconsidering%20adding%20regulations%20on%20the%20circumstances%20under%20which%20the%20Department%20may%20waive%20all%20or%20part%20of%20federal%20student%20loan%20debts%2C%26quot%3B%20suggesting%20it%20is%20looking%20at%20expanding%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20education%20secretary's%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20highlighted%20five%20key%20groups%20of%20borrowers%20it%20wants%20negotiators%20to%20discuss%20when%20considering%20the%20new%20plan%20for%20broad%20debt%20relief%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20who%20have%20seen%20their%20balances%20grow%20due%20to%20accrual%20of%20unpaid%20interest%2C%20leaving%20them%20with%20balances%20higher%20than%20what%20they%20originally%20borrowers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20who%20are%20eligible%20for%20forgiveness%20under%20programs%20like%20income-driven%20repayment%20but%20did%20not%20apply%20for%20those%20programs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20who%20took%20on%20debt%20for%20a%20school%20that%20did%20not%20prepare%20them%20to%20earn%20enough%20money%20post-grad%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20who%20entered%20repayment%20before%20some%20certain%20benefits%20became%20available%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20who%20are%20experiencing%20financial%20hardship%20and%20don't%20benefit%20from%20relief%20programs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch2%3ECan%20I%20participate%20if%20I'm%20not%20a%20negotiator%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20Negotiations%20will%20be%20livestreamed%2C%20and%20the%20department%20will%20publish%20a%20link%20to%20view%20the%20sessions%20closer%20to%20the%20date.%20Members%20of%20the%20public%20will%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20submit%20comments%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20day%2C%20and%20once%20a%20draft%20of%20the%20rule%20is%20published%20next%20year%2C%20there%20will%20be%20another%20period%20for%20public%20comment%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroad-student-loan-forgiveness-status-biden-next-step-debt-relief-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696009850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516fd00f5d0bb0019e5b9b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroad-student-loan-forgiveness-status-biden-next-step-debt-relief-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Education%20Department%20announced%20it's%20moving%20forward%20with%20the%20process%20to%20determine%20what%20the%20next%20broad%20student-debt%20relief%20proposal%20will%20look%20like.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroad-student-loan-forgiveness-status-biden-next-step-debt-relief-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anil%20Agarwal's%20Vedanta%20to%20split%20biz%20into%206%20companies%20to%20unlock%20value%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696009275000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-06%2F28%2Ffull%2F1687914076-9909.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-board-approves-plan-for-demerger-of-business-into-6-listed-entities-123092901183_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20every%20share%20of%20the%20company%2C%20stockholders%20to%20get%20one%20additional%20share%20of%20each%20of%205%20new%20entities%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-board-approves-plan-for-demerger-of-business-into-6-listed-entities-123092901183_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-board-approves-plan-for-demerger-of-business-into-6-listed-entities-123092901183_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-board-approves-plan-for-demerger-of-business-into-6-listed-entities-123092901183_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TB%20Drugs%20Shortage%3A%20113%20Global%20Bodies%20Write%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Seek%20His%20'Urgent'%20Intervention%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F13090926%2F25372378539_a8d4c4de68_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20many%20as%20113%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20776%20individuals%20from%20across%20the%20world%20have%20addressed%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20health%20minister%20Manshukh%20Mandaviya%20seeking%20urgent%20intervention%20in%20the%20issue%20of%20shortage%20of%20drugs%20for%20TB%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20drug-resistant%20TB%20patients%20in%20India%20(such%20as%20TB%20patients%20on%20whom%20the%20first%20line%20of%20TB%20drugs%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20and%20require%20advanced%20treatment)%20have%20been%20facing%20drug%20shortages%20for%20several%20months%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20piece%20capturing%20the%20voices%20of%20family%20members%20of%20TB%20patients%2C%20some%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20state%20TB%20officers%2C%20and%20multilateral%20organisations%20like%20the%20WHO.%20Although%20these%20stakeholders%20expressed%20grave%20concern%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20denied%20any%20such%20problem%20two%20days%20after%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%5C%22%3EUnprecedented%20TB%20Drugs%20Stock-Out%20in%20India%3A%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20Skips%20UN%20High-Level%20Meet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20health%20minister%20also%20skipped%20the%20UN%20high-level%20meeting%20on%20TB%20amidst%20this%20shortage.%20The%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20New%20York%20on%20September%2022.%20Now%2C%20these%20TB%20advocacy%20groups%20have%20written%20the%20letter%20from%20New%20York.%20The%20groups%20and%20individuals%20come%20from%20Kenya%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Zambia%2C%20Malawi%2C%20Uganda%2C%20Canada%2C%20Ghana%2C%20Cameroon%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20India%2C%20and%20several%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20the%20highest%20TB%20burden%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20disease%20prevalence%2C%20or%20any%20hindrance%20in%20disease%20treatment%20in%20India%2C%20would%20be%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20the%20global%20elimination%20of%20TB.%20The%20WHO%20aims%20to%20eliminate%20TB%20globally%20by%202030%20while%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20set%20the%20target%20for%202025%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20letter%20and%20list%20of%20signatories%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHon.%20Prime%20Minster%20Narendra%20Modi%20152%2C%20South%20Block%2C%3Cbr%3E%20Raisina%20Hill%2C%3Cbr%3E%20New%20Delhi-110011%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHon.%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%3Cbr%3E%20Minister%20for%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20%26amp%3B%20Chair%20of%20the%20Stop%20TB%20Partnership%20Board%20Room%20No.%20348%2C%20%E2%80%98A%E2%80%99%20Wing%2C%3Cbr%3E%20Nirman%20Bhavan%2C%20New%20Delhi-110011%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20York%2C%20September%2022%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20People%20with%20TB%2C%20treatment%20providers%2C%20medical%20practitioners%2C%20survivor%20activists%2C%20civil%20society%20organizations%2C%20academics%2C%20writers%20and%20health%20journalists%20urge%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Health%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20to%20take%20immediate%20steps%20to%20urgently%20address%20the%20issues%20of%20drug%20stock%20outs%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20TB%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20UN%20High%20Level%20Meeting%20on%20TB%20signed%20on%20a%20political%20declaration%20today%2C%20the%20country%20having%20the%20highest%20burden%20of%20TB%20and%20drug-resistant%20TB%20(DR-TB)%2C%20India%2C%20is%20now%20reporting%20chronic%20stockouts%20of%20anti-TB%20medicines.%20The%20frequent%20stockouts%20of%20anti-TB%20drugs%20threaten%20to%20undo%20gains%20made%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20TB%20programme%20and%20also%20make%20the%20ambitious%20targets%20India%20has%20set%20for%20herself%20%E2%80%93%20to%20eliminate%20TB%20by%202025%2C%20five%20years%20before%20the%20SDG%20goal%20%E2%80%93%20unattainable.%20Uninterrupted%20supply%20of%20medicines%20is%20the%20first%20step%20to%20preventing%20drug%20resistance.%20The%20current%20stockouts%20are%20forcing%20people%20to%20go%20without%20treatment%20at%20catastrophic%20cost.%20Rajjab%2C%20a%20driver%20working%20with%20a%20private%20carpool%20company%20in%20Mumbai%20recently%20explained%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnow%2C%20neither%20the%20government%20is%20able%20to%20provide%20me%20with%20the%20medicines%2C%20nor%20are%20they%20available%20at%20the%20medical%20stores%E2%80%9D%20and%20he%20asks%20%E2%80%9Cif%20my%20wife%20dies%2C%20who%20would%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20this%20crime%3F%E2%80%9D%20Those%20who%20can%20find%20and%20buy%20the%20drugs%20from%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20are%20feeling%20added%20out-of-pocket%20expenditure%20and%20the%20substantial%20financial%20burden%20on%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20facility%20level%2C%20the%20second%20line%20drug%20supply%20too%20has%20been%20erratic%20and%20there%20are%20reports%20that%20there%20is%20no%20supply%20of%20drugs%20for%20both%20multi%20drug%20and%20extensively%20drug%20resistant%20TB%20(XDR-TB)%20and%20states%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20procure%20the%20same%20locally.%20Drug%20stock%20outs%20at%20the%20state%20level%20may%20lead%20to%20further%20TB%20drug%20resistance%20in%20people%20who%20are%20forced%20to%20interrupt%20their%20treatment%2C%20which%20also%20means%20that%20their%20treatment%20may%20stop%20working%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20June%202023%2C%20there%20have%20been%20regular%20reports%20of%20stockouts%20of%20drugs%20used%20to%20treat%20TB%20and%20MDR-TB%20in%20several%20DOTS%20%26amp%3B%20DOTS-Plus%20Centres%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20persistent%20shortages%20have%20affected%20both%20first-%20and%20second-line%20TB%20drugs%2C%20including%20pediatric%20formulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20list%20of%20drugs%20that%20have%20been%20out%20of%20stock%2C%20since%20June%2C%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoxifloxacin%20(Lfx)%2C%20Cycloserine%20(Cs)%2C%20Linezolid%2C%20Clofazamine%2C%20Pyridoxine%2C%20Delamanid%20FGD-1st%20line%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20India%20has%20lagged%20behind%20most%20other%20high%20burden%20countries%20in%20implementing%20the%20new%20BPaL%2FM%20treatment%20that%20is%20recommended%20by%20WHO%20as%20the%20preferred%20regimen%20for%20MDR-TB%20and%20shorter%20TB%20preventive%20therapy%20with%203HP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20concerned%20group%20of%20TB%20activists%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20we%20call%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EUndertake%20emergency%20procurement%20and%20reallocation%20of%20stocks%20to%20DOTS%20%26amp%3B%20DOTS%20Plus%20centers%20experiencing%20stockouts%20and%20shortages%20of%20anti-TB%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EExpedite%20drug%20procurement%2C%20improve%20inventory%20management%2C%20and%20strengthen%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EEnsure%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUrgently%20roll%20out%20the%20shorter%2C%20simpler%2C%20more%20effective%2C%20new%20treatment%20BPaL%2FM.%20BPaL%2FM%20will%20not%20only%20improve%20patient%20outcomes%20but%20reduce%20risk%20of%20stockouts%20due%20to%20fewer%20medicines%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ESufficiently%20allocate%20resources%20at%20the%20center%20and%20the%20state%20level%20to%20ensure%20a%20consistent%20supply%20of%20TB%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EEstablish%20a%20system%20for%20monitoring%20and%20reporting%20on%20drug%20stock%20levels%20to%20prevent%20future%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUrgently%20convene%20a%20meeting%20with%20civil%20society%20and%20community%20members%20from%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20and%20local%20tuberculosis%20community%20is%20willing%20and%20eager%20to%20collaborate%20with%20the%20government%20and%20relevant%20stakeholders%20to%20find%20sustainable%20long-term%20solutions.%20The%20undersigned%20leaders%20of%20health%2C%20human%20rights%20organizations%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20worsening%20situation%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOrganizational%20Signatories%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ctable%3E%20%3Ctbody%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2237%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%3EOrganization%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22236%5C%22%3ECountry%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2237%5C%22%3E1%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%3EAdvocates%20of%20Hope%20for%20Community%20(AHFCO)%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22236%5C%22%3EKenya%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2237%5C%22%3E2%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%3EAMERICAS%20TB%20COALITION%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22236%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2237%5C%22%3E3%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2241