tent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Law%20Commission%20recommended%20the%20government%20not%20to%20tinker%20with%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20of%2018%20years%2C%20this%20age%20in%20India%20has%20varied%20widely%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20from%2010%20years%20in%201860%20to%2016%20years%20for%20females%20till%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20age%20of%20consent%20is%20the%20age%20at%20which%20a%20person%20is%20considered%20legally%20capable%20of%20agreeing%20to%20marriage%20or%20sexual%20intercourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20age%20is%20defined%20by%20statute%20and%2C%20at%20present%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20for%20sexual%20intercourse%20is%2018%20years%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20POCSO%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20in%202012%2C%20there%20was%20no%20age%20of%20consent%20defined%20separately%20for%20males%20and%20it%20was%20fixed%20by%20virtue%20of%20Section%20375%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20which%20defines%20%26quot%3Brape%26quot%3B.%20For%20females%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20was%2016%20years%20till%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERape%20being%20defined%20as%20a%20crime%20that%20can%20only%20be%20committed%20against%20a%20woman%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20for%20sexual%20intercourse%20was%20only%20defined%20for%20a%20female%2C%20under%20which%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20is%20immaterial%20and%20any%20sexual%20activity%20amounts%20to%20statutory%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20was%20no%20age%20of%20consent%20for%20males.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bchild%26quot%3B%20itself%20was%20not%20defined%20either%20under%20the%20IPC%20or%20the%20General%20Clauses%20Act%2C%201897.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20defined%20for%20a%20woman%20by%20virtue%20of%20Section%20375%20of%20the%20IPC%20defining%20%26quot%3Brape%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20had%20a%20chequered%20history%20with%20the%20age%20set%20at%2010%20years%20in%201860%20to%2018%20years%20as%20it%20stands%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%20submitted%20to%20the%20law%20ministry%2C%20the%20law%20panel%20gave%20a%20brief%20history%20of%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20in%20the%20country%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201860%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20for%20females%20stood%20at%2010%20years%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20in%201891%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20for%20a%20woman%20was%20raised%20to%2012%20years%20under%20Section%20375%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20public%20outcry%20caused%20by%20the%20Phulmoni%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhulmoni%20was%20an%2011-year-old%20girl%20who%20died%20of%20haemorrhage%20from%20a%20rupture%20of%20the%20vagina%20caused%20by%20her%20husband%20who%20had%20forced%20sex%20on%20her.%20The%20husband%20was%20held%20guilty%20of%20only%20causing%20grievous%20hurt%20by%20doing%20a%20rash%20or%20negligent%20act%20dangerous%20to%20life%20and%20sentenced%20to%20one%20year's%20rigorous%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20was%20raised%20to%2014%20years%20in%201925%20and%20to%2016%20years%20in%201940.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUp%20till%202012%2C%20when%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20was%20enacted%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20remained%2016%20years%20for%20females%20and%20there%20continued%20to%20be%20no%20age%20of%20consent%20defined%20for%20a%20male.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20minimum%20age%20of%20marriage%20was%2018%20years%20for%20women%20and%2021%20years%20for%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20marital%20rape%20exception%20in%20Section%20375%20has%20also%20witnessed%20changes%20over%20the%20years%20starting%20from%2010%20years%20in%201860%20to%2015%20years%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Figure%20For%20Different%20Countries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Convention%20on%20the%20Rights%20of%20the%20Child%20defines%20a%20child%20as%20any%20person%20below%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%20However%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20ranges%20from%2013%20to%2018%20years%20globally.%20The%20age%20of%20consent%20in%20Canada%20was%20raised%20from%2014%20to%2016%20years%20only%20in%202008%20in%20light%20of%20increased%20incidents%20of%20teenagers%20being%20lured%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20varies%20by%20state.%20Under%20the%20federal%20law%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20in%20the%20US%20is%2018%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20states%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20age%20of%20consent%2C%20there%20is%20a%20minimum%20age%20requirement%20and%20the%20criminality%20of%20sexual%20intercourse%20with%20an%20individual%20who%20is%20above%20the%20minimum%20age%20requirement%20and%20below%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20is%20dependent%20on%20the%20age%20differential%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20and%2For%20the%20age%20of%20the%20defendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20age%20of%20consent%20in%20Australia%20varies%20between%2016%20to%2017%20years%20depending%20on%20the%20state%20or%20territory.%20The%20age%20of%20consent%20in%20Japan%20was%2013%20years%20till%202023%20while%20the%20age%20of%20majority%20is%2020%20years%20and%20the%20minimum%20age%20for%20marriage%20for%20a%20man%20is%2018%20years%20and%2016%20for%20a%20woman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20is%2016%20years%20even%20though%20a%20child%20has%20been%20defined%20as%20a%20person%20under%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696008960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fmpojkr1k_court-generic-fourt-files-generic-files-in-court-pixabay_625x300_11_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-years-to-18-the-history-of-age-of-consent-in-india-4436742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2