a%20white%20shirt%20and%20black%20trousers%2C%20carrying%20a%20black%20bag%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20in%20Bhogal%20market%20on%20Sunday%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESrivas'%20mobile%20phone%20was%20tracked%20and%20the%20police%20found%20that%20it%20had%20been%20switched%20on%20at%20the%20ISBT%20in%20Kashmere%20Gate%20on%20Monday.%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20bus%20terminus%20showed%20Srivas%20buying%20a%20ticket%20at%208.40%20pm.%20The%20footage%20showed%20him%20carrying%20two%20bags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStakeout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Delhi%20Police%20team%20left%20for%20Chhattisgarh%20on%20Thursday%20itself%20and%20reached%20Smriti%20Nagar%20in%20Bilaspur%2C%20where%20Srivas%20lives%20in%20a%20rented%20home%2C%20with%20teams%20from%20the%20Durg%20Police%20and%20Raipur%20Police.%20The%20cops%20waited%20outside%20the%20house%20for%20the%20entire%20night%20and%20arrested%20Srivas%20when%20he%20reached%20home%20at%205.45%20am%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSrivas%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Bilaspur%20Police%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696004580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F1l3bk4eg_delhi-theft_625x300_26_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fjust-one-man-planned-executed-rs-25-crore-delhi-heist-another-thief-did-him-in-4436494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rs%2025-crore%20jewellery%20theft%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20biggest%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20recent%20memory%2C%20was%20planned%20and%20executed%20by%20just%20one%20man%20from%20Chhattisgarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fjust-one-man-planned-executed-rs-25-crore-delhi-heist-another-thief-did-him-in-4436494%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fjust-one-man-planned-executed-rs-25-crore-delhi-heist-another-thief-did-him-in-4436494%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fjust-one-man-planned-executed-rs-25-crore-delhi-heist-another-thief-did-him-in-4436494%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Trevor%20Noah's%20Show%20-%20A%20Blot%20On%20Bengaluru's%20Image%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20his%20fans%20laugh%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Emmy-winning%20comedian%20Trevor%20Noah%20was%20to%20perform%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20September%2027-28%20as%20part%20of%20the%20India%20tour%20'Off%20the%20Record'.%20Just%20a%20few%20minutes%20into%20the%20show%2C%20the%20comedian%20realized%20the%20poor%20sound%20system%20which%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20show%20on%20both%20days%2C%20much%20to%20the%20disappointment%20of%20the%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20show%2C%20scheduled%20for%207.30%20pm%2C%20opened%20about%2050%20minutes%20late.%20The%20opening%20act%20by%20standup%20comic%20Wilner%20Sylvince%20was%20not%20audible%20to%20the%20audience%20at%20the%20back%20and%20when%20Trevor%20came%20on%20stage%2C%20the%20audience%20kept%20complaining%20that%20they%20could%20not%20hear%20the%20lines.%20Trevor%20took%20a%20break%20saying%20that%20he%20would%20get%20the%20sound%20quality%20fixed.%20But%20when%20he%20returned%2C%20nothing%20had%20changed%20forcing%20him%20to%20announce%20that%20the%20show%20could%20not%20go%20on%20due%20to%20poor%20audio%20quality%20and%20that%20the%20tickets%20would%20be%20refunded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20shameful%20moment%20for%20India's%20IT%20city%20when%20Trevor%20later%20tweeted%3A%20%26quot%3BDear%20Bengaluru%20India%2C%20I%20was%20so%20looking%20forward%20to%20performing%20in%20your%20amazing%20city%20but%20due%20to%20technical%20issues%20we've%20been%20forced%20to%20cancel%20both%20shows.%20We%20tried%20everything%20but%20because%20the%20audience%20can't%20hear%20the%20comedians%20on%20stage%20there's%20literally%20no%20way%20to%20do%20a%20show.%20We'll%20make%20sure%20all%20ticket%20holders%20receive%20a%20full%20refund%20and%20again%20I'm%20so%20sorry%20for%20both%20the%20inconvenience%20and%20disappointment%20this%20has%20never%20happened%20to%20us%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fbvbhfshg_bengaluru-traffic_625x300_29_September_23.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D650%2Cheight%3D400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20eyewitnesses%2C%20the%20audience%20seated%20at%20the%20back%20could%20neither%20hear%20nor%20see%20the%20performance.%20Poor%20acoustics%20along%20with%20flat%20seating%20and%20the%20air-conditioners%20not%20working%20forced%20the%20world-renowned%20stand-up%20comedian%20to%20cancel%20the%20shows.%20The%20venue%20Manpho%20Convention%20Centre%2C%20near%20Manyata%20Tech%20Park%20in%20North%20Bengaluru%2C%20at%20best%20is%20meant%20for%20holding%20marriages%20and%20meetings.%20The%20convention%20hall%20is%20one%20big-sized%20hall%20and%20does%20not%20have%20an%20amphitheatre%20seating%20for%20a%20show%20like%20this.%20It%20is%20not%20even%20designed%20to%20provide%20superior%20acoustics%2C%20let%20alone%20world-class%20sound%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20packed%20audience%20present%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20instead%20of%20laughter%2C%20it%20was%20dismay%2C%20anger%20and%20tears%20galore.%20It%20is%20unbelievable%20that%20an%20event%20of%20this%20magnitude%20with%20a%20world-class%20artist%20can%20be%20organised%20at%20such%20a%20shoddy%20place%2C%20which%20at%20best%20is%20meant%20for%20holding%20marriages%2C%20meetings%20and%20cultural%20programmes.%20How%20did%20the%20organisers%20'BookMyShow'%20and%20Trevor's%20event%20team%20pass%20the%20venue%20for%20an%20international%20performance%20of%20this%20class%2C%20without%20testing%20the%20sound%20quality%20at%20the%20venue%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F557rckg_trevor-noah-bengaluru-show_625x300_29_September_23.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D650%2Cheight%3D400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20was%20held%20on%20the%20same%20day%20when%20Bengaluru%20saw%20one%20of%20its%20unprecedented%20traffic%20congestions%20on%20the%20Outer%20Ring%20Road%20that%20led%20to%20the%20venue.%20Many%20Bengalureans%2C%20who%20had%20paid%20between%20Rs%203%2C000%20and%20Rs%2012%2C500%20for%20the%20tickets%2C%20could%20not%20make%20it%20at%20all%20for%20the%20show.%20%C2%A0In%20fact%2C%20fans%20stuck%20in%20the%20jams%20seeing%20no%20hope%20of%20reaching%20the%20venue%20on%20time%2C%20were%20offering%20to%20resell%20their%20tickets%20on%20X%20at%20a%20much%20lower%20price.%20%C2%A0Trevor%20got%20a%20taste%20of%20Bengaluru's%20infamous%20traffic%20as%20he%20himself%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20which%20the%20show%20started%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrashanth%20G%20who%20was%20in%20the%20audience%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20Bengalurean%2C%20I%20couldn't%20be%20more%20embarrassed.%20We%20are%20proud%20of%20the%20accomplishments%20of%20our%20city%20as%20India's%20IT%20capital%20but%20going%20forward%20we'll%20think%20twice%20before%20boasting.%20At%20the%20venue%2C%20it%20wasn't%20only%20the%20sound%20system%20that%20failed%20us%20but%20even%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20toilets%2C%20malfunctioning%20of%20the%20air-conditioners%20let%20us%20down.%20We%20stay%20near%20the%20venue%20and%20therefore%20were%20happy%20that%20our%20travel%20time%20would%20be%20short.%20In%20hindsight%20when%20I%20critically%20evaluate%20the%20venue%20of%20such%20an%20event%20which%20had%20to%20host%20a%20world-famous%20celebrity%2C%20I%20feel%20the%20organisers%20grossly%20erred%20in%20their%20judgement%20of%20selecting%20this%20convention%20centre%20and%20not%20preparing%20the%20basic%20infrastructure%20to%20host%20an%20event%20which%20would've%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20global%20critics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20this%20fiasco%20will%20make%20global%20event%20managers%20more%20skeptical%20about%20our%20country's%20ability%20to%20organise%20programmes%20featuring%20international%20celebrities%20and%20performers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20our%20country%20hosted%20the%20recently%20concluded%20G20%20summit%20successfully%20with%20aplomb%20and%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20participating%20nations%20went%20back%20home%20with%20cherished%20memories.%20And%20here%20it%20was%20an%20event%20that%20was%20organised%20by%20a%20professional%20event%20management%20company%20which%20failed%20in%20meticulously%20planning%2C%20anticipating%20potential%20roadblocks%20and%20creating%20an%20unforgettable%20experience%20for%20the%20audience%20and%20the%20comedian%2C%20bringing%20irreparable%20disrepute%20to%20the%20city%20in%20front%20of%20the%20global%20audience%20via%20instantly%20impactful%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhere%20did%20the%20organisers%20fail%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20comedian's%20management%20team%20should%20have%20been%20more%20careful%20in%20choosing%20the%20Indian%20organisers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20choice%20of%20venue%20was%20surprising%20even%20to%20a%20Bengalurean.%20Manyata%20Tech%20Park%20which%20is%20adjacent%20to%20the%20venue%20-%20Manpho%20Convention%20Centre%20-%20is%20home%20to%20hundreds%20of%20companies%20which%20employ%20over%2050%2C000%20people.%20Traffic%20snarls%20across%20the%20location%20even%20on%20ordinary%20days%20