0hands%20and%20teach%20the%20suspect%20a%20lesson.%20Subha%20was%20taken%20into%20a%20room%20where%20he%20was%20physically%20tortured%20and%20his%20head%20tonsured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20eyewitness%2C%20who%20preferred%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20leader%20(Manoranjan%20Mal)%20was%20kicking%20him%20like%20a%20football.%20He%20was%20hungry%2C%20repeatedly%20asking%20for%20water.%20They%20were%20saying%20Lodhas%20are%20thieves.%20They%20must%20be%20taught%20a%20lesson.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Lodha%20Shabar%20community%20is%20categorised%20among%20one%20of%20the%2075%20%E2%80%98particularly%20vulnerable%20tribal%20groups%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20is%20assigned%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status.%20The%20particular%20tribe%20is%20looked%20at%20with%20suspicion%20and%20disparagingly%20branded%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98criminal%20tribe%E2%80%99.%20Like%20in%20this%20instant%20case%2C%20in%20the%20event%20of%20theft%20or%20crime%2C%20the%20needle%20of%20suspicion%20falls%20on%20the%20community%20members%20due%20to%20the%20decades-old%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubha%E2%80%99s%20lifeless%20body%20was%20discovered%20in%20front%20of%20his%20hut%20the%20following%20morning%2C%20bearing%20marks%20of%20injuries%20all%20over%20his%20body.%20Initially%2C%20local%20politicians%20attempted%20to%20pass%20it%20off%20as%20a%20case%20of%20suicide%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20boy%20had%20consumed%20poison.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20land%20to%20cultivate%2C%20no%20food%20to%20eat%2C%20why%20would%20we%20keep%20poison%3F%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20the%20leaders%20just%20kill%20us%3F%20We%20are%20Shabar%20Dalits%2C%20that%20is%20why%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebabus%3C%2Fem%3E%20(leaders)%20frame%20and%20kill%20us%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20lamented%20Subha%E2%80%99s%20mother%20Balika%20Nayek.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20so%20far%20arrested%20seven%20individuals%2C%20including%20Mal%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20instigating%20and%20participating%20in%20the%20lynching.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Lodha%20Shabar%20community%2C%20to%20which%20Shubh%20Nayek%20belonged%2C%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20last%20panchayat%20elections%2C%20which%20might%20have%20led%20to%20resentment.%20They%20have%20taken%20revenge%20now.%20Minister%20Dr.%20Manas%20Ranjan%20Bhunia%20has%20been%20sheltering%20the%20culprits.%20We%20want%20an%20impartial%20investigation%20and%20capital%20punishment%20for%20the%20culprits%2C%E2%80%9D%20demanded%20Geeta%20Hansda%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20Adhikar%20Manch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr.%20Manas%20Ranjan%20Bhunia%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20took%20the%20initiative%20to%20get%20the%20accused%20arrested.%20After%20beating%20the%20boy%20to%20death%2C%20he%20returned%20home%20and%20drank%20poison%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he%20had%20acid%20coming%20out%20of%20his%20mouth.%20Local%20panchayat%20members%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20this%20matter.%20I%20have%20instructed%20the%20police%20to%20take%20strict%20action%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20no%20politics%20involved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20Delhi%20to%20Sabang%2C%20sectarian%20and%20communal%20politics%20along%20with%20hatred%20for%20the%20poor%20is%20increasing%20day%20by%20day.%20This%20is%20a%20repercussion%20of%20brutal%20arrogance%20of%20power%20and%20ruthless%20majoritarianism%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Md%20Salim%2C%20secretary%20of%20CPI(M)%20West%20Bengal%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20has%20once%20again%20highlighted%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20Lodha%20Shabar%20community%20in%20the%20state%2C%20historically%20stigmatised%20and%20marginalised.%20The%20Lodhas%20primarily%20rely%20on%20gathering%20wild%20roots%2C%20tubers%2C%20and%20edible%20leaves%2C%20and%20hunting%20for%20sustenance.%20They%20are%20considered%20an%20economically%20disadvantaged%20tribe%20concentrated%20