-i-have-to-resume-student-loan-payments-debt-relief-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E12-month%20%26quot%3Bon-ramp%26quot%3B%20period%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20borrowers%2C%20during%20which%20missed%20payments%20will%20not%20be%20reported%20to%20credit%20agencies%2C%20will%20also%20still%20be%20in%20effect%20during%20a%20shutdown.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20a%20prolonged%20shutdown%20lasting%20more%20than%20a%20few%20weeks%20could%20substantially%20disrupt%20the%20return%20to%20repayment%20effort%20and%20long-term%20servicing%20support%20for%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20requires%20all%20federal%20agencies%20to%20prepare%20contingency%20plans%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20shutdown%2C%20which%20specifies%20the%20operations%20that%20will%20operate%20and%20the%20ones%20that%20will%20lapse%20in%20a%20time%20of%20limited%20appropriations.%20The%20Education%20Department%20has%20yet%20to%20release%20its%20updated%20plan%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-will-government-shutdown-affect-student-loan-payment-resumption-debt-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%202021%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated%20that%20federal%20loan%20servicing%20could%20continue%20%26quot%3Bfor%20a%20very%20limited%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20department's%20plan%20to%20resume%20payments%20next%20month%2C%20some%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20are%20continuing%20to%20push%20for%20a%20pause%20on%20payments%20if%20the%20government%20shuts%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20throw%20borrowers%20back%20into%20repayment%20with%20bad%20faith%20loan%20servicers%20and%20an%20under-staffed%20Department%20of%20Education%20is%20a%20recipe%20for%20disaster%20and%20would%20deeply%20undermine%20the%20progress%20we%20have%20made%20to%20advance%20economic%20justice%20for%20student%20loan%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Ayanna%20Pressley%20%3Ca%20href