%20at%20a%20think%20tank%2C%20Hudson%20Institute%2C%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20made%20some%20allegations%2C%20initially%20privately%20and%20then%20publicly%2C%20and%20our%20response%20to%20him%2C%20both%20in%20private%20and%20public%2C%20was%20that%20what%20he%20was%20alleging%20was%20not%20consistent%20with%20our%20policy.%20And%20that%20if%20he%20or%20his%20government%20had%20anything%20relevant%20and%20specific%20that%20they%20would%20like%20us%20to%20look%20into%2C%20we%20were%20open%20to%20looking%20at%20it.%20That's%20where%20that%20conversation%20is%20at%20this%20point%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerrorists%20Given%20Operating%20Space%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERamping%20up%20his%20attack%20on%20the%20Canadian%20government%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThen%20it%20became%20dormant%20but%2C%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20it%20has%20come%20back%20into%20play%20because%20of%20what%20we%20consider%20to%20be%20a%20very%20permissive%20Canadian%20attitude%20towards%20terrorists%2C%20extremists%2C%20people%20who%20openly%20advocate%20violence.%20And%20they%20have%20been%20given%20operating%20space%20in%20Canada%20because%20of%20the%20compulsions%20of%20Canadian%20politics.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Americans%2C%20perhaps%2C%20Canada%20looks%20very%20different%20but%20it%20depends%20where%20the%20shoe%20pinches.%20For%20us%20it%20has%20certainly%20been%20a%20country%20where%20organised%20crime%20from%20India%20mixed%20with%20trafficking%20in%20people%2C%20mixed%20with%20secessionism%2C%20violence%2C%20terrorism%20-%20it's%20a%20very%20toxic%20combination%20of%20issues%20and%20people%20who%20have%20found%20operating%20space%20there.%20So%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20tensions%20with%20Canada%2C%20which%20well%20preceded%20what%20Mr%20Trudeau%20said%2C%20actually%20come%20out%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Diplomats%20Unsafe'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20situation%20today%20is%20that%20Indian%20diplomats%20are%20unsafe%20going%20to%20the%20embassy%20and%20consulates%20in%20Canada%20and%20that%20they%20are%20publicly%20intimidated%2C%20which%20compelled%20India%20to%20suspend%20visa%20services%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20confirmed%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20about%20these%20issues%20with%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20and%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPressed%20for%20details%20of%20the%20meetings%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20put%20it%20this%20way%2C%20they%2C%20obviously%20shared%20US%20views%20and%20assessments%20on%20this%20whole%20situation%20and%20I%20explained%20to%20them%2C%20at%20some%20length%2C%20the%20concerns%20which%20I%20had.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20both%20came%20out%20of%20those%20meetings%20better%20informed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrudeau's%20Pitch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Montreal%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Justin%20Trudeau%20said%20that%20Canada%20is%20still%20committed%20to%20building%20closer%20ties%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20growing%20economic%20power%20and%20important%20geopolitical%20player.%20And%20as%20we%20presented%20with%20our%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%2C%20just%20last%20year%2C%20we're%20very%20serious%20about%20building%20closer%20ties%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Canada-based%20National%20Post%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20obviously%2C%20as%20a%20rule%20of%20law%20country%2C%20we%20need%20to%20emphasise%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20work%20with%20Canada%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20get%20the%20full%20facts%20of%20this%20(the%20Nijjar%20killing)%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Post%20quoted%20Trudeau%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20was%20killed%20in%20Surrey%20in%20the%20Canadian%20province%20of%20British%20Columbia%20on%20June%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696001220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F7ik9v3a_s-jaishankar-antony-blinken-twitter_625x300_29_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-jaishankar-says-canada-harbours-extremist-elements-spoke-about-it-to-us-leaders-jack-sullivan-and-antony-blinken-4436028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20says%20%26quot%3BCanada%20harbours%20extremist%20elements%26quot%3B%2C%20spoke%20about%20it%20to%20US%20leaders%20Jack%20Sullivan%20and%20Antony%20Blinken%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-jaishankar-says-canada-harbours-extremist-elements-spoke-about-it-to-us-leaders-jack-sullivan-and-antony-blinken-4436028%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-jaishankar-says-canada-harbours-extremist-elements-spoke-about-it-to-us-leaders-jack-sullivan-and-antony-blinken-4436028%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-jaishankar-says-canada-harbours-extremist-elements-spoke-about-it-to-us-leaders-jack-sullivan-and-antony-blinken-4436028%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20urges%20India%20to%20cooperate%20with%20probe%20into%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20separatist%20in%20Canada%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696001220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-antony-blinken-india_6302436.jpg%3F20230929164341%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-us-urges-india-to-cooperate-with-probe-into-killing-of-sikh-separatist-in-canada-12972541%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20secretary%20o