ed%20to%20ensuring%20your%20well-being.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20the%20rapidly%20evolving%20nature%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20university%20expressed%20its%20inability%20to%20provide%20answers%20to%20many%20of%20the%20pressing%20questions%20it%20raises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BU%20of%20T%20is%20proud%20to%20be%20home%20to%20more%20than%202%2C400%20international%20students%20from%20India%20who%20enrich%20our%20classrooms%20and%20campus%20life%2C%20and%20many%20more%20students%2C%20faculty%2C%20staff%2C%20librarians%20and%20alumni%20with%20ties%20to%20that%20country.%20We%20want%20to%20assure%20all%20impacted%20members%20of%20our%20community%20-%20and%20in%20particular%20international%20students%20-%20that%20you%20are%20welcome%20here%20and%20we%20are%20deeply%20committed%20to%20supporting%20your%20wellbeing.%20We%20encourage%20you%20to%20make%20use%20of%20the%20resources%20below%20if%20you%20need%20support%20or%20have%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20needs%20of%20international%20students%2C%20the%20university%20has%20introduced%20resources%2C%20including%20immigration%20and%20visa%20support%2C%20academic%20assistance%20services%2C%20and%20a%20dedicated%20mental%20health%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20academic%20support%20services%20include%20an%20undergraduate%20student%20help%20desk%20enabling%20students%20to%20connect%20with%20their%20faculty%20or%20college%20registrar%2C%20while%20graduate%20students%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20their%20department%20or%20the%20School%20of%20Graduate%20Studies%20for%20assistance.%20Additionally%2C%20personal%20support%20services%20include%20access%20to%20a%20mental%20health%20portal%20and%20the%20U%20of%20T%20Telus%20Health%20Student%20Support%2C%20offering%20round-the-clock%20support%20via%20phone%20or%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695999780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fdl3hlupo_student-representative-image_6