r%20Front%20of%20India%20(PFI)%20was%20banned%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20and%20PFI%20attacking%20an%20Indian%20soldier%20could%20foment%20trouble.%20They%20found%20the%20soldier%2C%2035-year-old%20Shine%20Kumar%2C%20in%20the%20outpatient%20section%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20all%20set%20to%20give%20his%20statement.%20But%20the%20police%20were%20suspicious%20since%20the%20moment%20they%20got%20the%20call%20to%20the%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20we%20are%20informed%20by%20the%20victims%2C%20their%20relatives%2C%20civilians%20or%20the%20hospital%20staff.%20But%20we%20got%20it%20through%20a%20media%20house%20and%20a%20YouTuber%2C%20which%20made%20us%20suspicious%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20inspector%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20suspicion%20increased%20after%20they%20saw%20Shine%20at%20the%20hospital.%20He%20did%20not%20have%20visible%20scratches%20on%20his%20body%2C%20his%20shirt%20was%20cut%20in%20a%20straight%20line%20and%20he%20was%20otherwise%20untouched.%20They%20took%20his%20statement%20and%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20six%20identifiable%20yet%20unknown%20persons%20for%20assaulting%20the%20soldier.%20But%20within%20hours%2C%20it%20unravelled%20that%20Shine%20had%20lied%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20become%20famous.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20lie%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Shine%20claimed%20he%20was%20attacked%20at%20a%20rubber%20estate.%20He%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20worked%20with%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Electronics%20and%20Mechanical%20Engineers%20(EME)%20Corps%2C%20stationed%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20was%20in%20Kadakkal%20on%20vacation%2C%20due%20to%20finish%20on%20September%2025.%20On%20the%20night%20of%20September%2024%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20he%20had%20organised%20a%20small%20gathering%20at%20his%20house.%20After%20dinner%2C%20he%20took%20his%20bike%20to%20meet%20his%20friend%20Joshy%20to%20give%20him%20Rs%201%2C000%20in%20cash.%20Joshy%2C%20according%20to%20Shine%2C%20had%20transferred%20the%20money%20using%20Google%20Pay%20and%20wanted%20Shine%20to%20withdraw%20it%20and%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20him.%20When%20Shine%20reached%20the%20Mukkada%20Government%20School%2C%20six%20people%20stopped%20him%20and%20told%20him%20an%20inebriated%20man%20needed%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EShine%20claimed%20that%20he%20accompanied%20the%20men%20to%20a%20rubber%20estate%20on%20the%20Mukkada%20Chanappara%20road%2C%20and%20upon%20reaching%2C%20one%20of%20the%20men%20kicked%20him%20from%20behind.%20Four%20other%20persons%20allegedly%20assaulted%20him%2C%20lifted%20him%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20tied%20his%20hands%20and%20closed%20his%20mouth%20with%20tape.%20Shine%20Kumar%20claimed%20they%20forced%20him%20face%20down%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20then%20lifted%20him%20up%20again.%20The%20men%20then%20tore%20his%20T-shirt%20in%20the%20back%20and%20wrote%20%E2%80%98PFI%E2%80%99%20using%20green%20paint%20that%20they%20carried%20with%20them%2C%20and%20left%20him%20there%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20then%20managed%20to%20reach%20the%20hospital.%20Based%20on%20his%20complaint%2C%20Kadakkal%20police%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECatching%20the%20bluff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20struck%20the%20police%20was%20that%20he%20had%20no%20injuries%20on%20his%20body%2C%20not%20even%20a%20scratch%2C%20no%20stains%20or%20signs%20of%20being%20attacked%20on%20his%20body%20and%20T-shirt.%20Mukkada%20is%20a%20central%20place%20and%20even%20if%20it%20had%20happened%2C%20someone%20%E2%80%93%20residents%20or%20passersby%20%E2%80%93%20must%20have%20noticed%20such%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20or%20heard%20the%20commotion%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kollam%20Police%20Chief%20Sunil%20ML.%20The%20police%20found%20discrepancies%20in%20Shine%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20events%2C%20especially%20regarding%20his%20statement%20about%20handing%20over%20cash%20to%20his%20friend%20Joshy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShine%E2%80%99s%20Google%20Pay%20details%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20not%20received%20money%20from%20Joshy.%20Mobile%20tower%20signals%20told%20the%20police%20that%20Joshy%20was%20actually%20at%20Shine%E2%80%99s%20house%20for%20dinner%20that%20night.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20party%20organised%20that%20night%20to%20celebrate%20the%20first%20birthday%20of%20Shine%E2%80%99s%20child%20and%20for%20Onam%20on%2028%2C%20which%20is%20celebrated%20in%20parts%20of%20Kerala.%20We%20found%20that%20they%20were%20together%20that%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20Inspector%20Rajesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20Joshy%20was%20questioned%2C%20he%20gave%20a%20different%20version.%20He%20told%20the%20police%20he%20was%20drunk%20and%20went%20to%20Mukkada%20as%20Shine%20had%20called%20him.%20Joshy%20did%20not%20reveal%20if%20they%20had%20dinner%20together.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Joshy%20confessed%20that%20he%20wrote%20%E2%80%98PFI%E2%80%99%20on%20Shine%E2%80%99s%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoshy%20admitted%20to%20the%20police%20that%20it%20was%20Shine%20who%20asked%20him%20to%20paint%20on%20his%20back.%20Shine%2C%20according%20to%20his%20friend%2C%20wanted%20to%20become%20famous.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20asked%20me%20to%20write%20%E2%80%98PFI%E2%80%99%20on%20his%20back.%20But%20I%20heard%20%E2%80%98DFI%E2%80%99%20and%20wrote%20the%20same.%20When%20I%20told%20him%20I%20wrote%20%E2%80%98DFI%E2%80%99%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20change%20it%20to%20%E2%80%98PFI%E2%80%99.%20Then%2C%20he%20gave%20me%20a%20blade%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20cut%20the%20shirt.%20He%20also%20asked%20me%20to%20beat%20him%2C%20but%20I%20said%20I%20was%20too%20drunk%20and%20could%20not%20do%20it.%20He%20then%20asked%20me%20to%20drag%20him%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20but%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it.%20Then%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20tie%20his%20hands%20with%20tape%2C%20and%20he%20himself%20stuck%20a%20tape%20on%20his%20mouth.%20He%20then%20asked%20me%20to%20leave%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshy%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpQxEILEtvgw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kadakkal%20police%20recovered%20the%20paint%2C%20brush%2C%20blade%20and%20tape%20from%20Joshy%E2%80%99s%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunil%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20they%20were%20sceptical%20about%20Shine%E2%80%99s%20story%20as%20the%20people%20associated%20with%20PFI%20in%20the%20area%20are%20few.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20and%20questioning%20two%20to%20three%20people.%20Currently%2C%20Shine%20and%20Joshy%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20remanded%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKadakkal%20police%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20booked%20under%20153A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups)%2C%20177%20(furnishing%20false%20information)%2C%20120B%20(punishment%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy)%2C%20465%20(punishment%20for%20forgery)%2C%20468%20(forgery%20for%20purpose%20of%20cheating)%2C%2037%20(co-operation%20by%20doing%20one%20of%20several%20acts%20constituting%20an%20offence)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20117(d)%20(false%20statement%20to%20a%20police%20officer)%20of%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20(KP)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20another%20soldier%20Prabhakaran%2C%20in%20a%20viral%20video%2C%20made%20a%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Faudio-clip-witnesses-dispute-jawan-s-claim-wife-was-stripped-mob-tn-178487%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efalse%20but%20more%20serious%20claim%20that%20his%20wife%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmolested%20and%20s