o%20critical%20environmental%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEntry%20to%20this%20competition%20is%20only%20allowed%20to%20individuals%20nominated%20through%20Prix%20Pictet%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20global%20network%20of%20over%20300%20nominators%20which%20includes%20critics%2C%20curators%2C%20and%20other%20specialists%20in%20the%20visual%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENominators%20are%20asked%20to%20recommend%20portfolios%20that%20have%20the%20power%20and%20artistic%20quality%20demanded%20by%20the%20prize.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20was%20founded%2C%20the%20organisation%20says%20that%20more%20than%205%2C000%20photographers%20have%20been%20nominated%2C%20%E2%80%9Call%20of%20whose%20work%20in%20one%20way%20or%20another%20testifies%20to%20the%20fragile%20state%20of%20our%20planet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20world%20facing%20unprecedented%20challenges%2C%20from%20social%20inequality%20to%20environmental%20crises%2C%20it%20was%20crucial%20to%20turn%20the%20lens%20towards%20humanity%20itself.%20The%20theme%20%3Cem%3EHuman%3C%2Fem%3E%20provides%20a%20platform%20to%20explore%20the%20complexities%2C%20vulnerabilities%2C%20and%20strengths%20of%20the%20human%20condition.%20It%20allows%20the%20artists%20to%20capture%20and%20communicate%20the%20stories%2C%20struggles%20and%20triumphs%20of%20individuals%20and%20communities%20around%20the%20globe%2C%E2%80%9D%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Prix%20Pictet%2C%20Isabelle%20von%20Ribbentrop%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20theme%2C%20Prix%20Pictet%20aims%20to%20foster%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20our%20shared%20humanity%20and%20inspire%20meaningful%20conversations%20about%20the%20issues%20that%20impact%20us%20all.%20Especially%20when%20thinking%20about%20the%20theme%20%3Cem%3EHuman%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20strongly%20believe%20that%20instead%20of%20the%20future%20of%20photography%2C%20we%20should%20think%20about%20photography%20of%20the%20future.%20The%20power%20of%20the%20image%20lies%20in%20its%20abili