e%20the%20need%20for%20immediate%20afforestation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20many%20aren%E2%80%99t%20much%20interested%20in%20this%20type%20of%20social%20work%20in%20my%20area%2C%20there%20are%20still%20some%20who%20visit%20and%20help%20me%20out.%20I%20hope%20someday%2C%20everyone%20realises%20the%20need%20for%20a%20green%20and%20clean%20environment%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F124279%2Fpics-first-snows-transform-kashmir-mystical-wonderland-look%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMother%20Nature%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20conserved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAuthored%20by%20Firdous%20Hassan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695994405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20daily%20wager%20turned%20'Father%20of%20Chinars'%2C%20Abdul%20Ahad%20Khan's%20mission%20to%20protect%20Kashmir%20Valley's%20iconic%20tree%20started%20in%20Hatmullah%2015%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331243%2Fdaily-wager-is-father-of-chinars-kashmir-valley-environment-real-hero%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thakur'%20Poem%3A%20Is%20BJP's%20Attack%20on%20Manoj%20Jha%20a%20Ploy%20to%20Deflect%20Attention%20from%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29183927%2FThe-Wire-23.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERaghavendra%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%C2%A0Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20MLA%20from%20Bihar%2C%20has%20threatened%20to%20behead%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20leader%2C%20Manoj%20Jha%2C%20following%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20a%20poem%20in%20his%20parliament%20speech%20which%20is%20critical%20of%20feudal%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20%5BManoj%20Jha%5D%20are%20a%20Brahmin.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20it.%20You%20have%20forgotten%20that%20I%20am%20also%20a%20Rajput.%20We%20will%20not%20even%20think%20for%20a%20second%20before%20beheading%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20RJD%20chief%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20came%20to%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20defence%2C%20warning%20those%20making%20statements%20against%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20opposing%20Jha%20for%20his%20innocuous%20quote%20should%20stay%20within%20their%20limits.%20Manoj%20Jha%20is%20an%20intellectual%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav.%20Jha%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20social%20work%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20recently%20passed%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%2C%20Jha%20quoted%20from%20Hindi%20litterateur%20Omprakash%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20poem%2C%20which%20opens%20with%20the%20following%20lines%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKuan%20Thakur%20ka%2C%20Paani%20Thakur%20kaa%2C%20Khet%20Khalihar%20Thakur%20ka%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20well%20belongs%20to%20Thakur%3B%20so%20do%20the%20water%20and%20all%20the%20farm%20fields)%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20The%20poem%20makes%20an%20appeal%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckill%20the%20Thakur%20within%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EValmiki%20uses%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98Thakur%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20poem%20symbolically%2C%20both%20to%20depict%20the%20prevailing%20feudal%20mindset%20of%20his%20time%20as%20well%20as%20to%20call%20upon%20people%20to%20fight%20oppression%20being%20perpetuated%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste.%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20poem%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20was%20to%20call%20upon%20those%20wielding%20power%20and%20authority%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20that%20%E2%80%9Cexploitative%20Thakur%E2%80%9D%20from%20their%20psyche%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20denial%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJha%E2%80%99s%20comments%20have%20set%20off%20a%20barrage%20of%20criticism%20from%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Thakur%20community%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20with%20BJP%20leaders%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20launching%20the%20attack%20on%20Jha.%20Several%20BJP%20leaders%20described%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20comments%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-Rajput%E2%80%9D.%20Senior%20BJP%20leader%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20directed%20his%20criticism%20at%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%2C%20asking%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20to%20apologise%20for%20his%20party%20colleague%E2%80%99s%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Row%20over%20Manoj%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20comments%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20have%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20is%20troubled%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-lok-sabha-hate-speech%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20episode.%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20communal%20slurs%20at%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%E2%80%99s%20MP%2C%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20in%20the%20parliament%20have%20once%20presented%20to%20the%20world%20the%20hate%20factory%20being%20run%20by%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%2C%20with%20the%20tacit%20support%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government.%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20RJD%20and%20JD%20(U)%20believe%2C%20will%20be%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20deflect%20the%20public%20attention%20from%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20comments%20and%20train%20its%20guns%20at%20the%20opposition%2C%20given%20that%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20RJD%2C%20is%20a%20constituent%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22111655%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-11.15.41-AM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22111655%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-11.15.41-AM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22111655%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-11.15.41-AM-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22111655%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-11.15.41-AM-1024x511.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22111655%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-11.15.41-AM-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674238%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%20speaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20close%20to%20them%2C%20sensed%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20using%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20recitation%20of%20%3Cem%3EThakur%20ka%20Kuan%3C%2Fem%3E%20poem%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20Biduri.%20First%2C%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20national%20vice%20president%2C%20Shivanand%20Tiwary%20described%20the%20interpretation%20of%20the%20poem%20as%20anti-Rajput%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfoolish%20and%20downright%20stupid%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJDU%E2%80%99s%20national%20president%2C%20Lalan%20Singh%2C%20strongly%20followed%20up%20on%20Tiwary%E2%80%99s%20comment%2C%20defending%20Jha.%20%E2%80%9CManoj%20Jha%20did%20no%20wrong%20by%20quoting%20%3Cem%3EThakur%20ka%20Kuan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Why%20is%20the%20question%20being%20raised%20on%20it%20after%20a%20week%20of%20Jha%20reciting%20the%20said%20poem%3F%20Jha%20has%20not%20hurt%20the%20sentiment%20of%20any%20community%20and%20has%20done%20no%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said%20in%20defence%20of%20the%20leader%20from%20RJD%2C%20which%20is%20in%20government%20in%20Bihar%20with%20its%20alliance%20partner%20JD(U)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20Lalu%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20intervening%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20defending%20Manoj%20Jha%2C%20the%20RJD%20and%20JDU%20leaders%20belonging%20to%20the%20Rajput%20community%20will%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20now%20and%20understand%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20RJD%20leader.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20opposition%20leaders%20should%20be%20cautious%20with%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20mastered%20the%20art%20of%20diverting%20attention%20from%20its%20failure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-has-exposed-the-real-face-of-the-bjp-beyond-pr-charm-offensives-studied-silences%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%20Has%20Exposed%20the%20Real%20Face%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Beyond%20PR%20Charm%20Offensives%2C%20Studied%20Silences%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20some%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20leaders%20have%20also%20lashed%20out%20at%20Jha.%20Chetan%20Anand%2C%20RJD%20MLA%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20people%2C%20where%20he%20lives%2C%20get%20to%20hear%20this%20(poem)%2C%20they%20will%20not%20let%20him%20come%20there%E2%80%A6.%20I%20am%20shocked%20that%20people%20there%20(Rajya%20Sabha)%20listened%20to%20it.%20I%20would%20have%20protested%20then%20and%20there%20had%20I%20been%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chetan%20said.%20Chetan%20is%20the%20son%20of%20strongman%20Anand%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20released%20from%20jail%20after%20serving%20a%20prison%20term%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20an%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20in%20the%201990s.%20Anand%20Mohan%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%2C%20JD(U)%20leader%20and%20MLC%2C%20also%20criticised%20Jha.%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20statements%20create%20division%20in%20the%20society.%20We%20are%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20who%20unites%20people%20from%20all%20religions%20and%20castes.%20Manoj%20Jha%20will%20get%20a%20befitting%20reply%20for%20this.%20This%20is%20an%20indecent%20statement.%20He%20should%20apologise%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20Rajput%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98BJP%E2%80%99s%20trap%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20criticism%20that%20young%20leaders%20from%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20are%20falling%20into%20%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20trap%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20issue%20while%20also%20reflecting%20their%20lack%20of%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201931%2C%20Munshi%20Premchand%20wrote%20a%20short%20story%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThakur%20ka%20Kuan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Through%20the%20characters%20of%20Gangi%20and%20her%20ailing%20husband%20Jokhu%20%E2%80%93%20the%20couple%20hailing%20from%20the%20untouchable%20community%20%E2%80%93%20the%20great%20storyteller%20commented%20on%20the%20stranglehold%20of%20a%20feudal%20lord%20on%20the%20means%20of%20livelihood%20in%20a%20village.%20Gangi%20is%20unable%20to%20draw%20water%20from%20a%20well%20belonging%20to%20a%20Thakur%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20ailing%20for%20long%2C%20is%20compelled%20to%20drink%20contaminated%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOmprakash%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20poem%2C%20%E2%80%98Thakur%20ka%20Kuan%E2%80%99%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20a%20follow-up%20on%20Premchand%E2%80%99s%20story%20on%20the%20exploitation%20of%20the%20Dalit%20communities%20and%20disproportionate%20control%20of%20the%20feudal%20classes%20on%20the%20means%20of%20livelihood%20in%20the%20rural%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20criticism%20that%20the%20current%20crop%20of%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20leaders%20lack%20the%20understanding%20that%20the%20second-generation%20socialist%20leaders%2C%20including%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20and%20Shivanand%20Tiwary%2C%20possess.%20Nitish%20was%20known%20for%20his%20reading%20habit%20when%20he%20was%20a%20student%20leader.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20read%20the%20complete%20writings%20of%20socialist%20icons%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%2C%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Lalu%20Yadav%20was%20not%20very%20studious%2C%20he%20gained%20an%20immense%20understanding%20of%20society%20as%20he%20was%20under%20the%20tutelage%20of%20Lohia%2C%20Narayan%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakuri%2C%20and%20others.%20He%20also%20took%20an%20active%20part%20in%20the%20movements%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20meant%20to%20free%20deprived%20sections%20from%20oppression.%20Lalu%20began%20his%20political%20career%20by%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20procession%20led%20by%20Shivanand%20Tiwary%20against%20Shankaracharya%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20the%20Dalits%20in%20the%20late%201960s.%20Tiwary%20is%20known%20to%20read%20and%20write%20regularly%20till%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Lalu%20defended%20Jha%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20launching%20the%20book%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESansad%20se%20Sadak%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20authored%20by%20Shivanand%20Tiwary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695994229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29183927%2FThe-Wire-23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthakur-poem-is-bjps-attack-on-manoj-jha-a-ploy-to-deflect-attention-from-ramesh-bidhuri%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20RJD%20MP's%20use%20of%20'Thakur%20ka%20Kuan'%20poem%20in%20his%20parliament%20speech%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20barrage%20of%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20described%20his%20comments%20as%20'anti-Rajput'.%20A%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Bihar%20has%20threatened%20to%20behead%20Jha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthakur-poem-is-bjps-attack-on-manoj-jha-a-ploy-to-deflect-attention-from-ramesh-bidhuri%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20Higher%20The%20Position...%26quot%3B%3A%20Vice%20President's%20Swipe%20At%20Ashok%20Gehlot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20has%20some%20advice%20for%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20who%20has%20been%20questioning%20the%20Vice%20President's%20frequent%20visit%20to%20the%20Congress-ruled%20state%20where%20the%20assembly%20election%20will%20be%20held%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20election%20campaign%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Neemrana%2C%20Mr%20Gehlot%20had%20objected%20to%20the%20Vice%20President's%20visit%20to%20five%20districts%20since%20the%20election%20is%20near%20and%20the%20visit%20would%20%26quot%3Bsend%20all%20kinds%20of%20message%2C%20which%20is%20not%20good%20for%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPoliticians%20should%20come%2C%20but%20please%20do%20not%20send%20the%20Vice%20President%3B%20it%20is%20a%20constitutional%20post.%20We%20respect%20the%20President%20and%20the%20Vice%20President.%20Yesterday%20the%20Vice%20President%20came%20and%20visited%20five%20districts.%20It%20is%20election%20season.%20If%20you%20come%20now%20it%20will%20send%20all%20kinds%20of%20message%20which%20is%20not%20good%20for%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gehlot%20told%20a%20gathering%20in%20Neemrana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20Dhankhar%20in%20an%20apparent%20response%20to%20Mr%20Gehlot%20said%20those%20in%20high%20positions%20should%20use%20responsible%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20higher%20the%20position%20a%20person%20holds%2C%20the%20more%20dignified%20his%20conduct%20should%20be.%20Making%20any%20comment%20to%20gain%20political%20advantage%20is%20not%20a%20good%20thing.%20I%20call%20upon%20everyone%20to%20be%20responsible%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20constitutional%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Vice%20President%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice%20President%20said%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20%26quot%3Bcontemplation%20and%20concern%20that%20some%20people%20make%20indecent%20comments%20on%20constitutional%20institutions%2C%20wearing%20political%20glasses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20not%20do%20this%3B%20such%20behaviour%20is%20against%20our%20cultural%20heritage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20not%20look%20at%20constitutional%20functionaries%20with%20a%20political%20prism%20to%20score%20political%20points.%20That%20is%20not%20acceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaw%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20had%20also%20asked%20Mr%20Gehlot%20whether%20the%20Vice%20President%20needs%20to%20take%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20permission%20for%20visiting%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20Vice%20President%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20why%20is%20he%20coming%20now%3F%20So%20the%20Vice%20President%20will%20come%20after%20getting%20permission%20from%20him%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Meghwal%20told%20reporters%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Gehlot%20is%20on%20an%20intensive%20campaign%20across%20Rajasthan%2C%20touching%2018%20districts%20and%20heading%20into%2038%20constituencies.%20It's%20also%20a%20part%20of%20%26quot%3BMission%202030%26quot%3B%20outreach%20where%20Mr%20Gehlot%20is%20talking%20about%20his%20vision%20for%20Rajasthan%20till%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Gehlot%20strategy%20has%20a%20soft%20Hindutva%20subtext%20as%20he%20will%20also%20visit%20important%20temples%20during%20this%20campaign.%20His%20schedule%20shows%20he%20will%20visit%20at%20least%2010%20prominent%20and%20local%20temples%20during%20the%20third%20leg%20of%20this%20nin