show%2F104046482.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Umar%20Khalid's%20Release%20Will%20Give%20Us%20Back%20a%20Friend%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F09142413%2FIMG_2301-Large.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENation-making%20is%20a%20metonymic%20act.%20Some%20aspects%20of%20the%20nation%20easily%20stand%20for%20the%20whole%2C%20while%20others%20are%20deemed%20exceptions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20M.S.S.%20Pandian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20what%20seems%20like%20a%20different%20country%2C%20Umar%20and%20I%20sat%20together%20for%20the%20M.A.%20History%20lectures%20in%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU).%20We%20were%20taught%20by%20redoubtable%20historians%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20on%20our%20faculty.%20For%20most%20of%20them%2C%20history%20was%20seldom%20about%20the%20past.%20It%20was%20often%20a%20metaphor%20for%20the%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%20could%20radiate%20hope%20for%20the%20future%2C%20or%20even%20send%20across%20a%20warning.%20A%20stray%20riot%20in%20a%20late%2019th%20century%20North%20Indian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eqasbah%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20contained%20lessons%20for%20what%20the%20country%20could%20eventually%20become.%20A%2020th%20century%20workers%E2%80%99%20strike%20that%20defied%20both%20British%20threats%20and%20nationalist%20requests%20for%20moderation%20was%20a%20lesson%20on%20how%20people%20made%20history.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeither%20Umar%20nor%20I%20were%20happy%20to%20merely%20study%20the%20past.%20Interpreting%20the%20world%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20change%20was%20necessary.%20As%20a%20budding%20academic%20and%20a%20student%20activist%2C%20Umar%20was%20especially%20eager%20to%20give%20voice%20to%20people%20who%20lived%20under%20state%20repression%20in%20%E2%80%98zones%20of%20exception%E2%80%99%3A%20Bastar%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20%E2%80%98Naxal-affected%E2%80%99%20areas%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUmar%20consistently%20demanded%20accountability%20from%20the%20state%2C%20and%20respect%20and%20recognition%20for%20the%20lives%20and%20struggles%20of%20people%20on%20the%20margins.%20Umar%E2%80%99s%20location%20as%20a%20Muslim%20in%20Hindu%20majority%20(though%20not%20yet%20overtly%20and%20unabashedly%20majoritarian)%20India%20put%20him%20at%20a%20unique%20vantage%20point%20to%20understand%20the%20struggles%20of%20those%20whose%20loyalties%20to%20the%20nation%20was%20suspect%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20known%20of%20Umar%20before%20I%20met%20him.%20His%20sister%20was%20my%20batchmate%20in%20St.%20Stephen%E2%80%99s%20College.%20She%20had%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20a%20brother%20who%20was%20into%20History%20and%20wanted%20to%20do%20a%20Ph.D.%20She%20was%20the%20one%20who%20introduced%20us%20during%20our%20college%20days%20and%20I%20was%20glad%20to%20have%20him%20as%20a%20classmate%20in%20JNU.%20We%20easily%20bonded%20over%20our%20shared%20interest%20in%20Subaltern%20Studies%2C%20Left%20politics%2C%20the%20conundrums%20of%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20cricket%2C%20a%20range%20of%20departmental%20activities%2C%20and%20our%20mutual%20dislike%20for%20apolitical%20intellectualism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20class%20chit-chats%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echai%20pe%20charcha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20public%20meetings%20and%20other%20political%20gatherings%2C%20were%20full%20of%20fun%2C%20laughter%20and%20passionate%20arguments.%20Both%20of%20us%20were%20a%20touch%20removed%20from%20electoral%20politics%20on%20campus%2C%20which%20perhaps%20shielded%20our%20friendship%20from%20its%20vicissitudes.%20I%20was%20drawn%20towards%20working%20class%20politics%20in%20the%20surrounding%20industrial%20areas%2C%20and%20Umar%20would%20always%20enquire%20about%20the%20emerging%20trends%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20the%20M.A.%20days%20were%20over%2C%20our%20meetings%20became%20less%20frequent.%20A%20close%20affinity%20had%20however%20been%20cemented.%C2%A0%20Never%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20elitist%20aspects%20of%20my%20college%2C%20and%20rightly%20so%2C%20he%20once%20complimented%20me%20through%20his%20younger%20sister%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20my%20college%20junior%2C%20%E2%80%98Akash%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20good%20products%20of%20your%20college!%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20similar%20life%20decision%20after%20our%20M.Phil.%20ensured%20a%20lasting%20bond%20between%20us.%20We%20belonged%20to%20an%20increasingly%20small%20tribe%20of%20students%20who%20chose%20to%20remain%20in%20JNU%20for%20their%20Ph.D.%20research%20rather%20than%20seek%20academic%20careers%20abroad.%20We%20both%20wished%20to%20remain%20politically%20engaged%20in%20India%2C%20and%20to%20take%20up%20the%20fight%20against%20a%20rapidly%20advancing%20fascism.%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20finally%20settled%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20said%20with%20his%20trademark%20grin.%20%E2%80%98We%20are%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhoomiputras%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20JNU!%E2%80%99%20Bhoomiputras%20(sons%20of%20soil)%20or%20not%2C%20I%20was%20indeed%20happy%20that%20our%20association%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20improbable%20as%20it%20may%20sound%20in%20these%20gloomy%20times%2C%20one%20of%20our%20key%20takeaways%20from%20those%20long%20lectures%20and%20tutorial%20discussions%20on%20History%20was%20that%20history%20is%20open-ended.%20It%20could%20be%20made%20and%20unmade%20by%20ordinary%20people.%20Indeed%2C%20despite%20the%20Delhi%20pogrom%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20which%20summarily%20ended%20the%20vibrant%20protests%20against%20the%20majoritarian%20and%20discriminatory%20citizenship%20laws%20enshrined%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcaa-npr-nrc-the-law-is-being-weaponised-against-the-constitution%5C%22%3ECitizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Umar%20and%20his%20fellow%20protestors%20had%20some%20astonishing%20achievements%20in%20their%20bags.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protests%20re-energised%20India%E2%80%99s%20flagging%20democratic%20spirit%20and%20gave%20it%20new%20dimensions.%20Muslims%20spoke%20as%20Muslims%20and%20for%20India%20on%20an%20unprecedented%20scale.%20Muslim%20women%20led%20and%20we%20the%20people%20followed.%20Barriers%20erected%20brick%20by%20brick%20since%201947%20and%20walls%20heightened%20since%201992%20began%20to%20collapse.%20Political%20forces%2C%20which%20want%20to%20erect%20permanent%20walls%20between%20communities%2C%20felt%20threatened.%20They%20put%20the%20leaders%20in%20jail.%20Umar%20was%20one%20of%20the%20many%2C%20but%20a%20significant%20one%2C%20for%20he%20had%20been%20threatened%20before%20and%20yet%20he%20had%20refused%20to%20stay%20quiet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F30153444%2Fkanhaiya-anirban-umar.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F30153444%2Fkanhaiya-anirban-umar.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F30153444%2Fkanhaiya-anirban-umar-300x160.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F30153444%2Fkanhaiya-anirban-umar-1024x547.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-274463%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUmar%20Khalid%20and%20Anirban%20Bhattacharya.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2F%20Vijay%20Verma%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202016%2C%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20had%20dared%20to%20question%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict.%20There%20was%20nothing%20extraordinary%20about%20it.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20time%20someone%20had%20questioned%20the%20courts%20or%20the%20government%20in%20an%20Indian%20university%20campus.%20This%20event%20however%20got%20unusual%20and%20politically%20motivated%20media%20coverage.%20The%20ensuing%20media%20trial%20gave%20us%20an%20icon%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Ravish%20Kumar%20and%20a%20bete%20noir%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Arnab%20Goswami%2C%20and%20it%20gave%20the%20government%20an%20enemy%3A%20Umar%20Khalid.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20subsequent%20ordeal%20did%20not%20hold%20him%20back%20from%20voicing%20his%20protest%20against%20the%20CAA%2FNRC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20colorful%20nation-wide%20protests%20were%20followed%20by%20an%20apocalyptic%20horror%20show%20in%20Delhi.%20Armed%20militias%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20North%20East%20Delhi%20and%20the%20police%20quickly%20blamed%20the%20protestors%20for%20it.%20They%20put%20together%20a%20case%20against%20so-called%20outsiders%20who%20had%20supposedly%20colluded%20with%20some%20local%20people%20to%20orchestrate%20the%20violence.%20Citizens%20who%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20protests%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20build%20solidarities%20across%20social%20locations%20against%20the%20rampaging%20majoritarianism%20now%20faced%20terror%20charges%20under%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20spoken%20to%20Umar%20a%20few%20days%20before%20he%20was%20detained.%20I%20had%20called%20him%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20possibilities%20of%20his%20arrest.%20%E2%80%98They%20are%20standing%20with%20the%20knife%20next%20to%20my%20throat%20%E2%80%93%20neither%20slashing%20my%20throat%2C%20nor%20retreating%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20had%20said.%20The%20blow%20indeed%20came%20a%20few%20days%20later.%20Gulfisha%20Fatima%2C%20Natasha%20Narwal%2C%20Devangana%20Kalita%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%20and%20others%20had%20already%20been%20arrested.%20The%20state%20took%20longer%20to%20arrest%20Umar%2C%20presumably%20to%20give%20itself%20some%20room%20to%20collate%20charges%20that%20could%20potentially%20imprison%20him%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20teaching%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University%20at%20that%20time.%20I%20started%20speaking%20to%20my%20students%20frequently%20about%20all%20these%20friends%20who%20were%20lodged%20in%20jail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%2011%20October%202021%2C%20the%20students%20organized%20a%20candle-light%20vigil%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20the%20anti-CAA%2FNRC%20activists%20and%20the%20repeal%20of%20repressive%20laws%20like%20UAPA.%20In%20what%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20landmark%20event%20that%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20student%20activism%20in%20the%20new%20University%20campus%2C%20hundreds%20of%20students%20marched%20across%20the%20campus%20following%20the%20vigil%20chanting%20the%20names%20of%20our%20incarcerated%20friends.%20When%20called%20upon%20to%20speak%2C%20I%20duly%20reminded%20the%20students%20and%20my%20colleagues%20that%20our%20friends%20were%20behind%20bars%20because%20they%20had%20dared%20to%20back%20their%20beliefs%20with%20action.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrue%20to%20his%20convictions%2C%20Umar%20has%20refused%20to%20be%20quiet%20even%20after%20his%20arrest.%20He%20has%20spoken%20on%20behalf%20of%20all%20Indian%20dissenters%20across%20caste%2C%20creed%20and%20religion%3B%20carrying%20his%20community%20identity%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20empowerment%2C%20assertion%20and%20unity%3B%20and%20not%20of%20subjugation%2C%20slavery%20and%20division.%20He%20has%20spoken%20on%20the%20politicisation%20of%20religion%20but%20not%20only%20on%20the%20politicization%20of%20religion%2C%20but%20also%20on%20Adivasi%20rights%2C%20caste%20atrocities%2C%20economic%20policies%20and%20so%20on.%20He%20has%20refused%20to%20stand%20only%20for%20the%20part%20that%20he%20has%20been%20allocated%20by%20the%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20state.%20He%20has%20dared%20to%20stand%20for%20the%20whole.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20absurd%20police%20cases%20have%20dragged%20on.%20Jail%2C%20rather%20than%20bail%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20the%20norm%20for%20the%20incarcerated%20dissenters%2C%20much%20like%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhima-koregaon-16-must-not-be-forgotten%5C%22%3Eput%20behind%20bars%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20many%20other%20lesser-known%20cases%20targeting%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%20and%20Muslims.%20Gulfisha%E2%80%99s%20bail%20order%20has%20been%20reserved%20since%20February%20this%20year.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fumar-khalid-the-historian-his-continued-imprisonment-is-a-loss-to-the-academic-world%5C%22%3EUmar%E2%80%99s%20bail%20hearing%20has%20been%20adjourned%20time%20and%20again%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20latest%20being%20a%20four-week%20adjournment%20on%2014%20September.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20read%20that%20Umar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fumar-khalid-on-his-two-years-in-jail-i-feel-pessimistic-at-times-and-also-lonely%5C%22%3Ewondered%20how%20our%20country%20had%20turned%20the%20wrong%20way%20so%20quickly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20too%20wonder%20how%20it%20all%20happened.%20But%20we%20both%20know%20that%20it%20did%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20day.%20We%20could%20see%20it%20coming%20during%20our%20formative%20years.%20I%20first%20visited%20Umar%E2%80%99s%20house%20with%20his%20sister%20who%20wanted%20to%20share%20with%20us%20the%20stories%20of%20intimidation%20and%20trauma%20that%20the%20neighbourhood%20was%20subjected%20to%20after%20the%20Batla%20House%20encounter.%C2%A0%20In%20those%20days%20we%20slowly%20realised%20that%20Indian%20democracy%20was%20far%20from%20perfect%20and%20needed%20urgent%20course-corrections%3B%20Umar%20perhaps%20realised%20it%20much%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20will%20indeed%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20right%20what%20has%20gone%20wrong.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20long%2C%20hard%20road%20but%20I%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20many%20people%20in%20our%20generation%20are%20prepared%20for%20the%20long%20march.%20Freedom%20for%20Umar%20and%20all%20other%20political%20prisoners%2C%20and%20the%20repeal%20of%20repressive%20laws%20like%20UAPA%2C%20will%20be%20important%20steps%20in%20our%20journey.%20Umar%E2%80%99s%20release%20will%20give%20us%20back%20a%20friend%2C%20and%20simultaneously%20strengthen%20our%20collective%20quest%20for%20freedom%20and%20democracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Akash%20Bhattacharya%2C%20former%20faculty%20member%20of%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20Bangalore%2C%20is%20a%20historian%20and%20a%20political%20activist%20affiliated%20to%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation).%20He%20was%20Umar%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20batchmate%20in%20JNU%20from%202009%20to%202018.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695991231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F09142413%2FIMG_2301-Large.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fumar-khalids-release-will-give-us-back-a-friend%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Umar%20has%20refused%20to%20be%20quiet%20even%20after%20his%20arrest.%20He%20has%20spoken%20on%20behalf%20of%20all%20Indian%20dissenters%20across%20caste%2C%20creed%20and%20religion%3B%20carrying%20his%20community%20identity%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20empowerment%2C%20assertion%20and%20unity%3B%20and%20not%20of%20subjugation%2C%20slavery%20and%20division.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fumar-khalids-release-will-give-us-back-a-friend%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Advisable%20To%20Tinker%20With%20Age%20Of%20Consent%26quot%3B%3A%20Law%20Commission%20To%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%20has%20advised%20the%20Centre%20against%20lowering%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20from%2018%20to%2016%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%2C%20arguing%20that%20doing%20so%20will%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20fight%20against%20child%20marriage%20and%20child%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20considers%20it%20necessary%20to%20bring%20about%20amendments%20in%20the%20Act%20to%20%26quot%3Bremedy%20the%20situation%26quot%3B%20in%20cases%20in%20which%20there%20is%20tacit%20approval%20from%20children%20aged%20between%2016%20and%2018.%20It%20said%20%26quot%3Bguided%20judicial%20discretion%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20applied%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20had%20urged%20parliament%20to%20address%20growing%20concerns%20related%20to%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Consent%20Can%20Be%20Manufactured'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Law%20Ministry%2C%20the%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20careful%20review%20of%20existing%20child%20protection%20laws%2C%20various%20judgements%20and%20considering%20the%20maladies%20of%20child%20abuse%2C%20child%20trafficking%20and%20child%20prostitution%20that%20plague%20our%20society%2C%20the%20Commission%20is%20of%20the%20measured%20view%20that%20it%20is%20not%20advisable%20to%20tinker%20with%20the%20existing%20age%20of%20consent%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20if%20there%20is%20automatic%20decriminalisation%20once%20the%20defence%20of%20consent%20is%20claimed%2C%20it%20must%20be%20kept%20in%20mind%20that%20consent%20can%20always%20be%20manufactured.%20The%20panel%20pointed%20to%20data%20which%20reflects%20that%20most%20perpetrators%20in%20POCSO%20cases%20are%20people%20known%20or%20close%20to%20the%20child%20and%20sometimes%20even%20people%20from%20the%20same%20family.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20diluting%20the%20law%20in%20this%20manner%20could%20mean%20reducing%20it%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bpaper%20law%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20the%20police%20investigation%20suffers%20from%20a%20great%20number%20of%20inadequacies%20and%20if%20it%20is%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20that%20get%20to%20determine%20if%20there%20was%20consent%20or%20not%2C%20then%20a%20lot%20of%20genuine%20cases%20that%20need%20to%20be%20prosecuted%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20may%20not%20see%20trial%20on%20account%20of%20investigating%20agencies%20themselves%20declaring%20them%20to%20be%20cases%20of%20consensual%20romantic%20sexual%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20a%20dilution%20will%20provide%20an%20easy%20route%20to%20reduce%20the%20cases%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20or%20deal%20with%20them%20without%20getting%20into%20the%20complexity%20of%20issues%20that%20surround%20such%20a%20trial%2C%20thereby%20reducing%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20to%20a%20'paper%20law'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeed%20For%20Amendments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%2C%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Ritu%20Raj%20Awasthi%2C%20former%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%2C%20said%20it%20had%20considered%20all%20the%20views%20and%20suggestions%20given%20in%20connection%20with%20cases%20involving%20those%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2016%20and%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Commission%20considers%20it%20necessary%20that%20certain%20amendments%20need%20to%20be%20brought%20in%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20to%20remedy%20the%20situation%20in%20cases%20wherein%20there%20is%20tacit%20approval%20in%20fact%20though%20not%20consent%20in%20law%20on%20part%20of%20the%20child%20aged%20between%2016%20to%2018%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20said%20it%20was%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20such%20cases%20do%20not%20merit%20being%20dealt%20with%20the%20same%20severity%20as%20cases%20that%20%26quot%3Bwere%20ideally%20imagined%20to%20fall%20under%26quot%3B%20the%20POCSO%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Commission%2C%20therefore%2C%20deems%20it%20fit%20to%20introduce%20guided%20judicial%20discretion%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20sentencing%20in%20such%20cases.%20This%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20law%20is%20balanced%2C%20thus%20safeguarding%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20the%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20are%20not%20binding%2C%20and%20will%20be%20studied%20and%20taken%20into%20consideration%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20will%20take%20a%20final%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Poses%20Difficult%20Questions'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20event%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20had%20spoken%20about%20judgments%20of%20the%20POCSO%20courts%20in%20'romantic%20cases'%20-%20involving%20consenting%20adolescents%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20are%20no%20doubt%20aware%2C%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20criminalises%20all%20sexual%20activity%20for%20those%20under%20the%20age%20of%2018%20regardless%20of%20whether%20consent%20is%20factually%20present%20between%20the%20two%20minors%20in%20a%20particular%20case.