s-wedding-heres-a-throwback-to-cousin-priyanka-chopra-and-nick-jonas-love-story%2Fphotostory%2F104044123.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman's%20Body%20Found%20In%20Bengal%20With%20Throat%20Slit%2C%20Face%20Burnt%20Off%3B%201%20Arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20arrested%20one%20person%20in%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20a%20woman%2C%20whose%20body%20was%20found%20with%20her%20hands%20and%20legs%20tied%2C%20throat%20slit%20and%20face%20burnt%20off%2C%20near%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20was%20found%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20in%20Gunrajpur%20village%20near%20the%20Swarupnagar%20border%20area%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20and%20the%20arrest%20was%20announced%20on%20Friday.%20Police%20said%20the%20victim%20is%20a%20young%20Bangladeshi%20woman%2C%20who%20used%20to%20work%20in%20a%20beauty%20parlour%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20returning%20home%20to%20Bangladesh%20and%20she%20may%20have%20been%20killed%20for%20money%2C%20%C2%A0Basirhat%20Police%20District%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Joby%20Thomas%20SK%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20people%20generally%20carry%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20money%20and%20ornaments%20while%20returning%20to%20Bangladesh.%20But%20nothing%20was%20found%20in%20the%20victim's%20bag%2C%20which%20was%20kept%20near%20the%20body.%20So%2C%20we%20suspect%20that%20those%20were%20looted%20from%20her%20before%20being%20murdered%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thomas%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20found%20a%20spectacle%20case%20bearing%20an%20address%20of%20Faridpur%20in%20Bangladesh%20from%20her%20bag%2C%20which%20helped%20them%20ascertain%20her%20identity.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20talked%20to%20her%20family%20members.%20They%20will%20be%20coming%20here.%20Details%20will%20emerge%20after%20we%20interrogate%20the%20arrested%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20was%20arrested%20from%20Bikhari%20village%20under%20Swarupnagar%20police%20station%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20intelligence%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20sure%20whether%20the%20victim%20entered%20India%20legally.%20We%20hope%20to%20get%20information%20on%20this%20after%20her%20family%20members%20reach%20here%20from%20Dhaka%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PTI%20report%20quoted%20Mr%20Thomas%20as%20saying.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20not%20revealed%20the%20cause%20of%20death%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20postmortem%20report%20is%20awaited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Attacks%20Trinamool%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20horrific%20incident%20has%20led%20the%20BJP%20to%20train%20its%20guns%20on%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20which%20it%20has%20accused%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20control%20-%20and%20even%20encouraging%20-%20violence%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20situation%20of%20law%20and%20order%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Tied-up%20body%20of%20a%20young%20woman%20with%20her%20throat%20slit%20and%20face%20charred%20beyond%20recognition%2C%20was%20found%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20from%20an%20orchard%20close%20to%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border%20in%20North%2024-Parganas.%20But%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20won't%20utter%20a%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20IT%20Cell%20Chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Malviya%20said%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20surprise%20if%20%26quot%3Bcriminals%20patronised%20by%20the%20TMC%26quot%3B%20are%20behind%20the%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IT%20Cell%20chief%20also%20attacked%20the%20Congress%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWill%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20quick%20to%20shed%20crocodile%20tear