20women's%20reservation%20bill%20before%20it%20was%20presented%20to%20President%20Murmu%20for%20her%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20amendment%20bill%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20near%20unanimity%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20with%20unanimity%20during%20a%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20law%20will%20take%20some%20time%20before%20being%20implemented%20as%20the%20next%20census%20and%20the%20subsequent%20delimitation%20(redrawing%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20constituencies)%20exercise%20will%20check%20the%20seats%20being%20kept%20aside%20for%20women%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20that%20without%20appropriate%20participation%20of%20women%20in%20politics%2C%20one%20cannot%20talk%20about%20inclusive%20society%20and%20democratic%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20BJP%20event%20after%20unveiling%20a%20statue%20of%20its%20ideologue%20Deendayal%20Upadhyaya%20on%20his%20birth%20anniversary%20on%20September%2026%20in%20Delhi%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20in%20Parliament%20is%20not%20only%20a%20win%20for%20democracy%20but%20also%20for%20the%20party's%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695988920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fm2ukr428_pm-modi-women-reservation-bill_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-gets-presidents-assent-days-after-historic-vote-becomes-law-4435467%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20has%20given%20her%20assent%20to%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20days%20after%20a%20historic%20vote%2C%20has%20become%20a%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-gets-presidents-assent-days-after-histor