ediate%20withdrawal%20at%20the%20WTO%20agricultural%20committee%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20countered%20this%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20new%20ban%20was%20a%20regulation%20rather%20than%20a%20restriction%2C%20which%20was%20crucial%20for%20the%20food%20security%20of%20its%201.4%20billion%20people%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fus-asks-india-to-lift-export-ban-on-non-basmati-rice-immediately%2Farticle67357746.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20pointed%20out%20at%20the%20WTO%20agriculture%20committee%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20granted%20exemptions%20from%20the%20export%20ban%20to%20those%20in%20need%20upon%20their%20governments%E2%80%99%20request%20and%20was%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20food%20security%20in%20those%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Geneva-based%20trade%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fus-asks-india-to-lift-export-ban-on-non-basmati-rice-immediately%2Farticle67357746.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20WTO%20members%20led%20by%20the%20US%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20export%20ban%20had%20a%20detrimental%20impact%20on%20countries%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20imports%2C%20particularly%20during%20times%20of%20crisis%2C%20as%20it%20accounted%20for%20roughly%2040%25%20of%20global%20exports.%20The%20other%20members%20questioning%20India%20included%20Japan%2C%20Australia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Thailand%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20currently%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fafter-basmati-exports-centre-places-curbs-on-all-varieties-of-rice-india-ships-overseas%5C%22%3Erestrictions%20of%20varying%20degrees%20on%20all%20varieties%20of%20rice%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20ships%20overseas.%20The%20Union%20government%20in%20July%20had%20placed%20a%20ban%20on%20export%20of%20non-basmati%20rice%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20%241200-price%20floor%20on%20the%20export%20of%20Basmati%20rice%20and%20a%2020%25%20duty%20on%20export%20of%20parboiled%20rice%20in%20August.%20India%20had%20also%20banned%20overseas%20sales%20of%20the%20broken%20variety%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20banning%20non-basmati%20rice%20export%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20said%20that%20some%20shipments%20would%20be%20allowed%C2%A0%20on%20request%20to%20meet%20the%20food%20security%20needs%20of%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-the-rice-export-ban-by-india-has-achieved%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20Rice%20Export%20Ban%20by%20India%20Has%20Achieved%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECiting%20information%20from%20its%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20the%20US%20stated%20that%20India%20was%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20record%20estimated%20rice%20production%20of%20134%20million%20tonnes%20and%20stocks%20of%2036%20million%20tonnes%20for%20the%202023-24%20period%2C%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20US%20said%20that%20under%20the%20conditions%20of%20ample%20domestic%20supply%2C%20the%20new%20export%20ban%20created%20unnecessary%20trade%20barriers%20and%20hindered%20the%20flow%20of%20food%20to%20areas%20where%20it%20is%20most%20needed.%20It%20said%20that%20it%20would%20encourage%20India%20to%20lift%20the%20export%20ban%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20India%20maintained%20that%20the%20ban%20was%20put%20in%20place%20keeping%20in%20mind%20domestic%20food%20security%20and%20was%20periodically%20reviewed%20to%20allow%20necessary%20adjustments%20based%20on%20domestic%20demand%20and%20supply%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20providing%20advance%20notifications%20for%20restrictions%2C%20India%20argued%20that%20it%20could%20not%20do%20so%20as%20it%20may%20lead%20to%20private%20players%20manipulating%20market%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695981721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F03164309%2FDSC2224-1024x684-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fwto-us-calls-indias-rice-export-ban-unnecessary-india-says-food-security-priority%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20maintained%20that%20the%20ban%20was%20put%20in%20place%20keeping%20in%20mind%20domestic%20food%20security%20and%20was%20periodically%20reviewed%20to%20allow%20necessary%20adjustments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fwto-us-calls-indias-rice-export-ban-unnecessary-india-says-food-security-priority%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manchester%20United%20player%20Antony%20to%20return%20to%20duties%20despite%20abuse%20allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695981660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-antony-manchester-united_6280019.jpg%3F20230910131343%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmanchester-united-player-antony-to-return-to-duties-despite-abuse-allegations-12972293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manchester%20United%20footballer%20Antony%20will%20resume%20training%20at%20the%20club%20and%20will%20be%20available%20for%20selection%20despite%20abuse%20allegations%20being%20brought%20against%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A143%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmanchester-united-player-antony-to-return-to-duties-despite-abuse-allegations-12972293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com