%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29144518%2FF7JO8M9WkAAekVE.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20was%20no%20mention%20in%20the%20official%20readout%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20diplomatic%20spat%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20featured%20in%20the%20meeting%20between%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20and%20US%20secretary%20of%20state%20Antony%20Blinken%20in%20Washington.%20However%2C%20US%20media%20reports%20claimed%20that%20the%20topic%20did%20figure%20in%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20September%2028%2C%20Jaishankar%20and%20Blinken%20met%20at%20the%20State%20Department%20in%20the%20US%20capital%20of%20Washington%20D.C.%2C%20but%20neither%20side%20mentioned%20whether%20the%20controversy%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20about%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20was%20discussed.%20However%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Findia-canada-blinken-biden-jaishankar-ddd5985d8686bec6c8d43ac487aabd6c%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWASHINGTON%2520(AP)%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520Secretary%2520of%2Ca%2520Sikh%2520activist%2520in%2520Canada.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20Reuters%20reported%20that%20it%20was%20raised%20and%20Blinken%20reiterated%20that%20New%20Delhi%20should%20cooperate%20with%20the%20Canadian%20investigation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBlinken%20raised%20the%20Canadian%20matter%20in%20his%20meeting%2C%20(and)%20urged%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20cooperate%20with%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fcanada-pm-says-he-is-sure-blinken-will-raise-murder-case-with-india-2023-09-28%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20a%20US%20official%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interaction%20at%20the%20Hudson%20Institute%20think-tank%20on%20Friday%2C%20Jaishankar%20confirmed%20whether%20the%20issue%20came%20up%20during%20his%20talks%20with%20Blinken.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20did%E2%80%9D.%20The%20US%20side%20shared%20its%20assessments%20on%20this%20whole%20situation%20and%20he%20explained%20to%20the%20Americans%20a%20summary%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20concerns%2C%20he%20noted.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20hopefully%20we%20both%20came%20out%20better%20informed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20as%20per%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20Mathew%20Miller%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fsecretary-blinkens-meeting-with-indian-external-affairs-minister-jaishankar-7%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussed%20a%20full%20range%20of%20issues%2C%20including%20key%20outcomes%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20presidency%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%20and%20its%20potential%20to%20generate%20transparent%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20high-standard%20infrastructure%20investments%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%20they%20covered%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccontinued%20importance%20of%20cooperation%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%202%2B2%20Dialogue%2C%20in%20particular%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20defense%2C%20space%2C%20and%20clean%20energy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20start%20of%20the%20discussions%2C%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20that%20he%20looked%20forward%20to%20welcoming%20Blinken%20for%20the%20%E2%80%982%2B2%E2%80%99%20dialogue%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20official%20press%20release%20from%20the%20Indian%20govern