other%20religion.%20The%20committee%20called%20for%20their%20identification%20and%20for%20them%20to%20be%20protected%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20they%20are%20still%20intact%20or%20have%20been%20vandalised%2C%20damaged%20or%20burned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Manipur%20police%20had%20said%20that%20least%205%2C172%20cases%20of%20arson%2C%20including%204%2C786%20houses%20and%20386%20religious%20places%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-death-toll-violence-missing-arms%5C%22%3Ewere%20reported%20in%20the%20last%20four%20months%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20committee%20is%20headed%20by%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20high%20court%20Chief%20Justice%20Gita%20Mittal.%20It%20also%20has%20former%20Bombay%20high%20court%20judge%20Shalini%20P.%20Joshi%20and%20former%20Delhi%20high%20court%20judge%20Asha%20Menon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20committee%20has%20considered%20the%20contents%20of%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Meitei%20Christian%20Churches%20Council%2C%20Manipur%2C%20which%20had%20alleged%20that%20%E2%80%9C240-247%E2%80%9D%20churches%20were%20vandalised%2C%20looted%20and%20burnt%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695979838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F13105808%2FScreenshot-2023-05-13-at-10.58.03-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-appointed-panel-asks-manipur-govt-to-protect-places-of-worship-buildings-of-displaced%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20additionally%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20of%20all%20properties%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-appointed-panel-asks-manipur-govt-to-protect-places-of-worship-buildings-of-displaced%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%2