-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992-460x1024.jpeg%20460w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992-689x1536.jpeg%20689w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.01-1695822992-150x334.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EISRO%20rocket%20models%20made%20by%20Craftizan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%20while%20my%20father%20wanted%20me%20to%20take%20a%20government%20job.%20Since%20model%20making%20was%20not%20commercially%20viable%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20do%20woodwork.%20After%20my%20engineering%2C%20I%20learnt%20woodwork%20from%20workshops%20doing%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Mysuru%20resident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20he%20set%20up%20a%20woodworking%20business%20in%20Pune.%20He%20did%20interior%20design%20and%20made%20furniture%20and%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20after%20a%20few%20years%2C%20where%20he%20continued%20his%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20set%20up%20a%20place%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20our%20business%20flourished.%20We%20had%20almost%20150%20people%20working%20for%20us.%20We%20did%20different%20kinds%20of%20furniture%20and%20designed%20many%20houses.%20However%2C%20we%20had%20to%20shut%20shop%20due%20to%20some%20financial%20difficulties%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ramji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20one%20to%20be%20buoyed%20down%20by%20difficulties%2C%20he%20started%20doing%20interior%20design%20consulting%20from%202002.%20But%20his%20heart%20lay%20in%20model%20making.%20After%20moving%20to%20Mysuru%2C%20he%20would%20unwind%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20by%20making%20his%20miniature%20models%20of%20trains%20and%20rockets%20at%20home.%20This%20hobby%20workshop%20grew%20with%20time%