many%20engineering%20college%20students%20from%20Mysuru%20have%20visited%20Ramji%E2%80%99s%20factory%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20only%20done%2010%20percent%20of%20the%20work%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20do%20so%20far.%20Ninety%20percent%20of%20it%20is%20left.%20I%20want%20to%20propagate%20engineering%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20Children%20tend%20to%20pick%20up%20things%20early.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20Meccano%20like%20sets%20or%20kits%20to%20spur%20this%20interest.%20This%20teaches%20them%20basic%2C%20fundamental%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengineering%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20hopes%20that%20one%20day%2C%20a%20young%20child%20would%20be%20inspired%20by%20his%20kits%2C%20like%20the%20Meccano%20set%20did%20for%20him%20all%20those%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20interested%20in%20purchasing%20a%20model%2C%20contact%206363321706%2F%208147553286%2F%209964982545%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695823519000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ramji%20Swaminathan%20from%20Mysuru%20has%20turned%20his%20love%20for%20model%20making%20into%20a%20business.%20He%20builds%20rocket%2C%20and%20satellite%20models%20for%20ISRO%20through%20his%20venture%2C%20Craftizan%20engineering%20models.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A598%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331067%2Framji-swaminathan-craftizan-miniature-models-of-isro-rockets-satellites-chandrayaan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Startup%20Helping%20Indians%20Reap%20the%20Benefits%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20In%20Their%20Mother%20Tongues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20small%20village%20of%20Raghurajpur%20in%20Odisha%2C%20vibrant%20colours%20and%20intricate%20artistry%20fill%20every%20corner.%20This%20charming%20place%2C%20also%20called%20%E2%80%98Raghurajpur%20Art%20Village%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20%3Cem%3EPatachitra%3C%2Fem%3E%20painters%2C%20whose%20detailed%20artwork%20decorates%20the%20village%20and%20attracts%20visitors%20from%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20their%20art%20is%20greatly%20admired%2C%20the%20village%20artisans%20have%20struggled%20with%20poverty%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESwarnalata%20Nayak%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20this%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317479%2Fart-historian-anitha-n-works-with-siddi-women-to-sell-kavandi-quilts-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20artisan%20community%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20spent%20her%20early%20married%20life%20looking%20after%20her%20in-laws%20and%20children.%20Wanting%20to%20send%20her%20children%20to%20a%20good%20school%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20join%20her%20husband%20in%20the%20craft%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20money%20coming%20into%20the%20house%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20send%20my%20children%20to%20a%20good%20school.%20However%2C%20even%20after%20the%20two%20of%20us%20started%20working%20together%2C%20we%20were%20still%20not%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20fees%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20toil%20and%20dedication%20of%20these%20artisans%20are%20often%20met%20with%20meagre%20wages.%20Swarnalata%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20wages%20can%20plummet%20as%20low%20as%20Rs%201%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20which%20is%20hardly%20enough%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%E2%80%9D%20Balancing%20household%20chores%20and%20contributing%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20craftwork%20had%20become%20increasingly%20taxing%20for%20Swarnalata.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20something%20changed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20Karya%20Project%20and%20suggested%20I%20get%20involved.%20The%20work%20is%20quite%20simple%3B%20all%20I%20have%20to%20do%20is%20speak%20in%20Odiya%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20it%20gets%20recorded%2C%20and%20then%20I%20get%20paid!%E2%80%9D%20Swarnalata%20informs%20that%20she%20was%20paid%20Rs%204%2C000%20after%20working%20for%20just%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%202021%20by%20Manu%20Chopra%20and%20Vivek%20Seshadri%2C%20with%20Safiya%20Husain%20joining%20a%20year%20later%2C%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20Karya%20Project%20uses%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F119176%2Fhow-rural-indians-can-get-same-opportunities-as-urban-counterparts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erural%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%20find%20respectable%20work.%20Workers%20use%20the%20%E2%80%98Karya%E2%80%99%20app%20to%20record%20audio%20in%20their%20native%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Karya%20Project%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpecialised%20AI%2C%20like%20large%20language%20models%20like%20Chat%20GPT%2C%20primarily%20uses%20English%20due%20to%20the%20abundance%20of%20text%20and%20audio%20data%20available.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20need%20for%20databases%20containing%20languages%20spoken%20in%20India%20other%20than%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20Chat%20GPT%20were%20to%20operate%20in%20Kanada%2C%20the%20AI%20would%20require%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20audio%20and%20text%20data%20for%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Karya%20Project%20steps%20into%20this%20role%20by%20collecting%20and%20selling%20such%20data%20in%20different%20languages%20to%20its%20clients.%20However%2C%20what%20sets%20the%20project%