%20Akshay%20spoke%20to%20caregivers%2C%20doctors%20and%20visited%20old-age%20homes.%20He%20also%20spoke%20to%20parents%20of%20children%20with%20disabilities%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20most%20people%20with%20dementia%20or%20children%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20tracking%20devices%20on%20them%2C%20which%20makes%20things%20difficult.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20caregivers%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20stressed%20they%20get%20when%20their%20loved%20one%20walks%20off.%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20solid%20for%20them%2C%20which%20is%20a%20fool-proof%20way%20of%20finding%20their%20child%2C%20or%20parent%2C%20or%20spouse%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Akshay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20people%20are%20also%20unable%20to%20communicate%20effectively.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20QR%20tags%20are%20an%20insurance%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Akshay.%20%E2%80%9CI%20created%20this%20mechanism%20so%20that%20the%20identification%20process%20is%20sped%20up%20and%20the%20missing%20citizens%20can%20come%20home%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20log%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprojectchetna.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20click%20on%20register%2C%20fill%20in%20the%20personal%20details%20of%20the%20person%20you%E2%80%99re%20making%20it%20for%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20get%20the%20QR%20pendant.%20Anyone%20with%20a%20phone%20can%20scan%20the%20code%20and%20get%20the%20information.%20Akshay%20is%20also%20building%20technology%20that%20will%20alert%20you%20when%20anyone%20scans%20the%20QR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20if%20someone%20from%20Mumbai%20has%20wandered%20off%20to%20Bengaluru.%20If%20someone%20there%20scans%20the%20QR%2C%20you%20will%20get%20a%20notification.%20This%20will%20help%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20who%20go%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20need%20for%20empathy%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCozNGI2oRDP%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCozNGI2oRDP%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCozNGI2oRDP%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EHe%20named%20his%20project%20%E2%80%98Chetna%E2%80%99%20as%20it%20means%20consciousness%20and%20because%20it%20is%20aimed%20at%20helping%20those%20people%20who%20have%20%E2%80%98lost%20their%20consciousness%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329441%2Fchennai-startup-bookwater-tracks-water-cans-quality-with-qr-codes-helps-access-safe-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQR-based%20digital%20identification%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20Akshay%20Rs%20200%20to%20make%20each%20pendant%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20given%20away%20100%20of%20these%20for%20free%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMumbai%20resident%20Rajagopal%2C%20whose%2015-year-old%20son%20is%20on%20the%20autism%20spectrum%2C%20first%20found%20out%20about%20this%20product%20through%20a%20friend.%20Upon%20hearing%20about%20it%2C%20he%20found%20that%20it%20was%20a%20well%20thought%20out%20and%20sensitive%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20son%20went%20missing%20for%20just%2010%20minutes%20in%20a%20zoo%2C%20it%20was%20a%20horrendous%20experience%20for%20us.%20I%20had%20also%20seen%20a%20child%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20local%20train%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20lost.%20I%20immediately%20handed%20him%20over%20to%20the%20railway%20police%20at%20Vikhroli%20station.%20Such%20a%20QR%20tag%20is%20very%20beneficial%20for%20children%20on%20the%20spectrum%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkshay%20had%20previously%20created%20such%20QR%20tags%20for%20stray%20dogs%20as%20well%2C%20in%20February%202023.%20He%20was%20triggered%20to%20do%20this%20after%20his%20dog%20went%20missing.%20This%20particular%20QR%20code%20gives%20the%20name%2C%20gender%2C%20caretaker%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20phone%20number%20and%20vaccination%2Fsterilisation%20history%20of%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20both%20these%20innovations%20are%20much-needed%2C%20they%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20awareness%20to%20succeed%20on%20a%20grand%20scale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20authorities%2C%20especially%20the%20railway%20police%2C%20need%20to%20be%20told%20about%20these%20QR%20codes.%20A%20lot%20of%20awareness%20is%20needed%20to%20make%20people%20acquainted%20with%20this%20product.%20Above%20all%2C%20people%20need%20to%20have%20a%20little%20more%20empathy%2C%20and%20be%20more%20forthcoming.%20When%20you%20see%20someone%20in%20distress%2C%20you%20need%20to%20try%20and%20help%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rajagopal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETarun%20Gupta%2C%20who%20went%20missing%20in%20October%202019%2C%20has%20still%20not%20been%20found.%20Akshay%20hopes%20to%20prevent%20any%20other%20parent%20from%20going%20through%20such%20a%20harrowing%20ordeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20out%20more%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fprojectchetna.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F36637034%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENCBI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworldpopulationreview.com%2Fcountry-rankings%2Fmissing-persons-statistics-by-country%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWorld%20population%20review%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695385883000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshay%20Ridlan%20has%20come%20up%20with%20a%20QR-based%20digital%20identification%20system%20to%20locate%20people%20who%20lose%20their%20way.%20His%20innovation%2C%20a%20pendant%20with%20a%20QR%20code%20in%20it%2C%20would%20be%20beneficial%20for%20people%20with%20dementia%20and%20Alzheimer's%20and%20children%20with%20disabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330545%2Fakshay-ridlan-qr-code-locket-finding-lost-missing-people-dementia-autism-upsc%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Retd%20Army%20Major%26nbsp%3Bis%20on%20a%20Mission%20to%20Make%20Adventure%20Sports%20Inclusive%20for%20People%20With%20Disabilities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20points%20in%20our%20lives%2C%20we%20all%20grapple%20with%20the%20timeless%20existential%20question%3A%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20life%3F%E2%80%99%20For%20Major%20Vivek%20Jacob%2C%20this%20profound%20question%20surfaced%20after%20dedicating%20more%20than%2015%20years%20of%20his%20life%20to%20serving%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20have%20either%20been%20living%20in%20the%20past%20or%20in%20the%20future.%20For%20once%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20the%20present%20and%20find%20what%20I%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Vivek%20(44)%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDesiring%20a%20respite%20from%20the%20demands%20of%20life%20and%20yearning%20to%20%E2%80%9Csit%20on%20a%20mountain%2C%20read%20books%2C%20and%20disconnect%20from%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Major%20Vivek%20Jacob%20contemplated%20early%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20given%20my%20country%20and%20my%20work%20all%20that%20I%20could.%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20for%20me%20to%20move%20on%20to%20a%20different%20facet%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20However%2C%20as%20unpredictable%20as%20life%20can%20be%2C%20this%20choice%20took%20the%20major%20down%20a%20path%20he%20may%20have%20never%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20he%20runs%20an%20organisation%20called%20CLAW%20Global%20(Conquer%20Land%2C%20Air%2C%20Water)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20impact%20venture%20working%20towards%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306209%2Fbengaluru-ngo-gives-horticulture-training-to-people-with-disability-provides-